INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(34,14,'ZHTW','虛弱．再見月之廢墟(日)','這是一套由 Namco Bandai 發行的 Wii平台專用「廢墟探險角色扮演類」遊戲，遊戲以人類滅亡的未來末日世界為背景，城鎮因為失去人類的維持，而逐漸變為渺無
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(35,15,'EN','Petz Horse Club','Can you raise, care, and love your own pet horse? Tame Wild Mustangs: Go on an adventure discovering and caring for wild horses. Ride with a Friend: Collect hidden bonuses with a pal and redeem cool unlockable items. Care for Your Very Own Foal: Gain the trust of your foals and horses as you raise, nurture, and love them. The Ultimate Horse Adventure!');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(36,16,'EN','Madden NFL 10','Madden NFL 10 epitomizes what fun looks like on the Wii, delivering the most social and dynamic experience from the franchise to date.
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(37,17,'EN','Madden NFL 10','For more than two decades, the Madden NFL series has delivered an authentic pro football experience steeped in all the aggressive power, strategy and emotion of the NFL. With Madden NFL 10 for the Wii, the legendary franchise roars back into action, combining NFL authenticity with thrilling multiplayer fun that lets you revel in the excitement of pro football. Gather the gang for a cooperative trip down the road to the Super Bowl, or compete in an epic battle to determine who among your circle of friends is the ultimate Madden player as Madden NFL 10 steeps you in the world of the NFL as only John Madden can.
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(38,17,'FR','Madden NFL 10','A vous les joies du football américain avec Madden NFL 10 sur Wii. Effectuez des captages de ballons spectaculaires comme un vrai receveur avec les mouvements de réception. Grâce aux contacts en défense vous pouvez réaliser des blocages bas, arracher les ballons ou couper les passes avec des contacts aériens. Créez votre propre franchise NFL : érigez votre stade, fixez des prix de concession, recrutez votre personnel, draftez des joueurs et dirigez toute cette entreprise de bout en bout.');
