INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(41,18,'ZHTW','太鼓達人Wii(日)','《太鼓之達人 Wii》是 Wii  平台上的首款作品，將採用遊戲與專屬太鼓控制器與鼓棒同梱方式推出，透過 Wii  遙控器擴充槽來與主機連接，透過敲擊太鼓控制器的方式來體驗與大型電玩版相同的玩法，之外也支援控制器按鈕輸入玩法。 
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(42,19,'EN','Don King Boxing','Experience boxing action both inside and outside the ring. Don King Presents Prizefighter is equal parts sports simulation and true boxing drama. The action within the squared-circle accurately mimics the sport''s tactics and hard knocks by letting you create angles and openings using a full arsenal of true 3D motion captured movement and punch mechanics found only in the real world sport? until now. Outside the ring, the drama continues as you are faced with temptations inherent in any professional athletes'' life, where you must balance these trappings of notoriety with the hardship of training in order to find the road to glory. As you progress through your career, a live-action documentary tells your story, warts and all. 14 fight gyms and arenas including the renowned Madison Square Garden, Trump''s Taj Mahal, and Boardwalk Hall in Atlantic City. Multiplayer lets you go head-to head against your opponents on the same machine or online to see who is the better fighter pound-for-pound.');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(43,19,'DE','Don King Boxing','Mit 2K Sports erleben Sie die Action im Boxring wie nie zuvor!
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(44,20,'EN','Don King Boxing','Experience boxing action both inside and outside the ring. Don King Presents Prizefighter is equal parts sports simulation and true boxing drama. The action within the squared-circle accurately mimics the sport''s tactics and hard knocks by letting you create angles and openings using a full arsenal of true 3D motion captured movement and punch mechanics found only in the real world sport? until now. Outside the ring, the drama continues as you are faced with temptations inherent in any professional athletes'' life, where you must balance these trappings of notoriety with the hardship of training in order to find the road to glory. As you progress through your career, a live-action documentary tells your story, warts and all. 14 fight gyms and arenas including the renowned Madison Square Garden, Trump''s Taj Mahal, and Boardwalk Hall in Atlantic City. Multiplayer lets you go head-to head against your opponents on the same machine or online to see who is the better fighter pound-for-pound.');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(45,20,'FR','Don King Boxing','Don King Boxing est un jeu de boxe sur Wii. Entraînez-vous, suivez une évolution progressive de votre personnage et devenez le meilleur boxeur de tous les temps. Le titre vous propose différents modes de jeu pour vous aguerrir et gagner de l''expérience pour vos combats. Faites les bons choix et les sacrifices pour accéder à l''élite mondiale.');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(46,20,'DE','Don King Boxing','Erlebe, wie es ist, ein echter Profiboxer zu sein. Die Wii Balance Board-Funktionalität mit über 20 lizenzierten Boxern, ein umfassender Karrieremodus, Trainings-Minispiele und aufregende Multiplayer-Matches ermöglichen es dir, so tief wie nie zuvor in den Boxsport einzutauchen.
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(47,21,'EN','Hula Wii: Minna De Fura Oodorou','By utilizing the Wii Balance Board, players can take Hula lessons right in front of the television and learn how to shake, gesticulate, and dance like a native Hawaiian. In addition to the tutorials, the software also includes footage of dancers doing the Hula in the classic style. A video travelogue developed with the participation of the Hawaii Tourism Authority is also included on the Wii DVD which shows off the sights and natural beauty of Hawaii. ');
