INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(103,41,'ZHTW','用Wii玩銀河戰士Prime2黑暗回聲(日)','本作是一款以主角薩姆斯的視點來進行遊戲的第一人稱冒險遊戲。遊戲中以因巨大隕石衝擊而將行星分離成光、闇兩世界的地方為背景。薩姆斯展開了新的戰鬥。一邊穿梭在光、闇兩世界中，若一邊世界有所變化，另外一邊世界也會被影響到，玩家可利用這種特質來解開過程中的謎團。
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(104,42,'EN','AC/DC Live: Rock Band Track Pack','AC/DC LIVE: Rock Band Track Pack is a fully-featured, standalone extension to the multi-million unit selling, genre-defining, cultural phenomenons Rock Band and Rock Band 2, the ultimate social music game experiences. AC/DC Live lets you and your friends relive AC/DC''s epic 1991 live performance at Donington, UK, through the eyes of Brian Johnson, Angus Young, Malcolm Young, Cliff Williams, and Chris Slade.');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(105,43,'EN','AC/DC Live: Rock Band Song Pack','');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(106,43,'FR','AC/DC Live: Rock Band Song Pack','AC/DC Live: Rock Band Track Pack n''est rien de moins que le pack de chansons indispensable à tout fan de rock sur Wii. Vous y retrouvez 18 classiques de ce groupe mythique en live. Entre autres les célèbres Highway to Hell, For Those About too Rock ou encore Hells Bells et Thunderstruck.');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(107,44,'EN','Rock Band Country Track Pack','Rock Band Country Track Pack is a standalone software product from the creators of Rock Band and Rock Band 2. The Rock Band platform lets you and your friends form your own band and live out your rock and roll fantasies to music’s greatest soundtrack—now with a down-home country twang!
