INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(109,45,'JA','三國志 11 With パワーアップキット','コーエーの看板タイトル、歴史シミュレーションゲーム「三國志」シリーズがＷｉｉに初登場！広大な中国を１枚の３Ｄマップで表現。吸収合併システムや、新施設の加わった内政、戦法を駆使した戦闘などを駆使して中国統一を果たそう。また、Ｗｉｉリモコンを使用した「必殺アクションモード」で武将さなながらの一騎討ちも楽しめる。');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(110,45,'ZHTW','三國志 11 威力加強版(日)','《三國志》是 KOEI 取材自古典小說名作「三國演義」所製作的策略模擬遊戲，以中國東漢末年三國割據的歷史題材為主題，融合國政經營與謀略戰爭的要素，玩家將扮演活躍於三國時代割據一方的諸侯或各勢力麾下的謀臣武將，為了統一天下成就霸業而努力。
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(111,46,'EN','Story Hour: Adventures','Classic fairy tales and fables had been passed down from generation to generation verbally and in books. Those traditions are now getting an interactive twist in the Story Hour series. A modern take on such beloved tales as Cinderella, Snow White, Jack and the Beanstalk, and Paul Bunyan, these tales offer four different stories that incorporate motion sensitive controls so that parents and preschoolers can tell stories together. Story Hour: Adventures features four classic stories: Paul Bunyan (illustrated by Stan Chow), Jack & The Beanstalk (illustrated by Simon Scales), Aladdin (illustrated by David Gordon) and The Three Brothers (illustrated by Constanza Basaluzzo.)');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(112,47,'EN','Story Hour: Adventures','Classic fairy tales and fables had been passed down from generation to generation verbally and in books. Those traditions are now getting an interactive twist in the Story Hour series. A modern take on such beloved tales as Cinderella, Snow White, Jack and the Beanstalk, and Paul Bunyan, these tales offer four different stories that incorporate motion sensitive controls so that parents and preschoolers can tell stories together. Story Hour: Adventures features four classic stories: Paul Bunyan (illustrated by Stan Chow), Jack & The Beanstalk (illustrated by Simon Scales), Aladdin (illustrated by David Gordon) and The Three Brothers (illustrated by Constanza Basaluzzo.)');
