INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(141,60,'EN','Go Play Circus Star','The circus is in town, and you’re the star! Go Play Circus Star lets you step into the shoes of a circus performer whose job is to wow the crowd with death defying stunts, animal tricks and sleight of hand. As part of Majesco’s new Go Play line, Circus Star delivers a motion-based experience that the entire family can enjoy together! 
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(142,61,'EN','Metroid Prime: Trilogy','Metroid Prime 3: Corruption set a new standard for first-person motion controls in video games. Now it''s bringing those controls to the rest of the celebrated series, allowing players to experience the entire Metroid Prime story arc with the peerless precision of the Wii Remote. Nintendo announces Metroid Prime Trilogy, a new premium three-game collection for the Wii console that bundles all three landmark Metroid Prime games onto one disc and revamps the first two installments with intuitive Wii Remote controls, wide-screen presentation and other enhancements. Each game maintains its original storyline and settings, but now Metroid Prime and Metroid Prime 2: Echoes lets you use your Wii Remote to aim with precision as heroine Samus Aran. Based on the breakthrough control system that debuted in Metroid Prime 3: Corruption, these new Wii controls bring an entirely new level of immersion and freedom to these milestone games ');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(143,62,'EN','Metroid Prime Trilogy','Metroid Prime 3: Corruption set a new standard for first-person motion controls in video games. Now it''s bringing those controls to the rest of the celebrated series, allowing players to experience the entire Metroid Prime story arc with the peerless precision of the Wii Remote. Nintendo announces Metroid Prime Trilogy, a new premium three-game collection for the Wii console that bundles all three landmark Metroid Prime games onto one disc and revamps the first two installments with intuitive Wii Remote controls, wide-screen presentation and other enhancements. Each game maintains its original storyline and settings, but now Metroid Prime and Metroid Prime 2: Echoes lets you use your Wii Remote to aim with precision as heroine Samus Aran. Based on the breakthrough control system that debuted in Metroid Prime 3: Corruption, these new Wii controls bring an entirely new level of immersion and freedom to these milestone games.');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(144,62,'FR','Metroid Prime Trilogy','METROID PRIME.
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(145,62,'DE','Metroid Prime Trilogy','Die Zukunft hat begonnen! 
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(146,62,'ES','Metroid Prime Trilogy','Tres de las aventuras de la cazarrecompensas Samus Aran, repletas de mitología, cargadas de emocionante exploración y acción explosiva, se han reunido en un solo disco para que vivas la acción en primera persona como siempre debió ser.
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(147,63,'EN','Guilty Gear XX Accent Core Plus','The fighting franchise that launched an entirely new style of fighting games is celebrating its 10th anniversary with the most complete and definitive version of the game on the Nintendo Wii. Follow the stories of the 25 crazy combatants and dish out a mind-numbing amount of insane combos that the series is known for.');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(148,64,'EN','Speed Racer: The Videogame','Take the wheel and GO! It''s a fight to the finish as you compete at amazing speeds, racing as your favorite Speed Racer characters. Perform tricks and pull off insane stunts through incredible, twisting stadium tracks, all while fighting against rival racers with incredible Car-Fu action! Play more than 19 characters from the film featuring the voices of Emile Hirsch as Speed Racer, Matthew Fox as Racer X, and Christina Ricci as Trixie. High-speed action going over 400 MPH as you race through amazing stadiums tracks featuring loops, corkscrews, jumps and more. Master Car-Fu combat and fight your way to the finish by smashing, jumping, flipping and spinning other cars off the track Split-screen multi-player racing on the Wii lets you take on…or take out…your friends.');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(149,65,'EN','Speed Racer','');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(150,65,'JA','スピード・レーサー','');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(151,65,'ZHTW','極速賽車手(日)','本遊戲是由 2008 年美國華納兄弟公司製作的同名電影改編而來，遊戲的開發部分則由鈕西蘭的 Sidhe 負責，該工作室曾開發過在各平台都很受歡迎的《重力賽車》。據 Sidhe 稱， 玩家可以在遊戲中使用電影中登場的全部角色以及他們的愛車，並且也將完美還原電影中賽車比賽的激烈場面。');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(152,66,'EN','Speed Racer','Take the wheel and GO! It''s a fight to the finish as you compete at amazing speeds, racing as your favorite Speed Racer characters. Perform tricks and pull off insane stunts through incredible, twisting stadium tracks, all while fighting against rival racers with incredible Car-Fu action! Play more than 19 characters from the film featuring the voices of Emile Hirsch as Speed Racer, Matthew Fox as Racer X, and Christina Ricci as Trixie. High-speed action going over 400 MPH as you race through amazing stadiums tracks featuring loops, corkscrews, jumps and more. Master Car-Fu combat and fight your way to the finish by smashing, jumping, flipping and spinning other cars off the track Split-screen multi-player racing on the Wii lets you take on…or take out…your friends');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(153,66,'FR','Speed Racer: Le Jeu Vidéo','Bouclez votre ceinture et enfoncez l''accélérateur dans un jeu de course en cinémascope sur Wii. Tiré du film du même nom, Speed Racer vous met au volant d''un bolide pour faire le plein de sensations. Mettez le turbo et passez tous les obstacles qui se dressent devant vous.
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(154,67,'EN','Spider-Man: Web of Shadows','A deadly symbiote invasion brings devastation to New York City. In Spider-Man: Web of Shadows, the game is set in an apocalyptic vision of the city. You''ll have complete control over New York City''s salvation and the fate of Spider-man. It also features an all-new combat system that allows for three-dimensional battles that can start on the street and end up on rooftops. You can also switch between the red and black Spider-Man suits, choose to ally with Marvel''s heroes or villains and decide what missions to undertake to save Manhattan from destruction.
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(155,68,'EN','Spider-Man: Web of Shadows','When a deadly symbiote invasion devastates the streets of New York City, only Spider-Man can seize control and bring the city salvation. From the game''s direction and outcome through to Spider-Man''s destiny, Spider-Man: Web Of Shadows puts control in the player''s hands.
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(156,68,'FR','Spider-Man: Le Règne des Ombres','Spider-Man: Le Règne des Ombres est un jeu d''action sur Wii. Le titre vous permet de pouvoir alterner entre l''agilité du costume rouge ou la puissance du costume noir de Spider-Man. Vos choix ont un impact direct sur l''histoire et sur la façon dont vous êtes vu par les habitants. Il est également possible de débloquer des pouvoirs surpuissants et de créer des nouveaux combo.');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(157,68,'IT','Spider-Man: Il Regno delle Ombre','');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(158,69,'EN','Top Spin 3','Compete against the pros with Top Spin 3. Play online or offline to rise in the ranks against current top ranked professional players. This is a visually and physically realistic tennis experience. Using next generation technology, gameplay and graphics, Top Spin 3 features dynamic weather changes, evolutionary player visuals and comprehensive online offerings. With a unique user-generated component, you can also use new player creator features that include free-form body sculpting, makeup and tattoos.
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(159,70,'EN','Top Spin 3','For the 1st time ever on the Wii, play with or against 16 of the world''s top tennis pros at 10 real-life courts. Take advantage of complete Wii Remote™ functionality to perform forehands, backhands and serves exactly as you would swing a real racquet. Compete in addictively fun multi-player mini-games or rise through the ranks in Career Mode to become the #1 player in the world. 
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(160,70,'FR','Top Spin 3','La télécommande Wii a déjà permis à des millions de personnes de devenir des stars du tennis chez elles et désormais, vous allez pouvoir jouer avec les vraies stars des courts dans Top Spin 3 sur Wii.
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(161,70,'DE','Top Spin 3','2K Sports präsentiert erstklassiges Lineup aktueller und legendärer Tennisstars für Top Spin 3. 
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(162,71,'EN','Deer Drive','Deer Drive meshes hunting simulation with arcade style pick-up-and-play action and pacing for an exciting gaming experience. Deer Drive is the first deer hunting game that features two-player simultaneous play. Additionally, Deer Drive features a multitude of game play modes, including four player party mode, true-to-life sound effects, passive and aggressive prey, and a slew of hunting weapons.
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(163,72,'EN','Deer Drive','');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(164,72,'FR','Deer Drive','Ah, le plaisir de chasser du cerf virtuel, de l''ours de pixels, des canards modélisés à la perfection. C''est ce que nous propose ce Deer Drive sur Wii. C''est donc par beau temps ou sous une pluie battante que vous devrez chasser l''animal, le traquer avec trois amis ou non et puis au moins, ça ne fera de mal à personne.');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(165,73,'EN','Sam & Max: Season One','It''s a vile world out there. Get too complacent and all sorts of weirdos start coming out of the woodwork. Good thing Sam & Max are here to hose down the sleaze and keep some kind of peace. Violently, if possible. Who are these irreverent crime fighters? Sam''s a six-foot tall canine shamus with a love of justice. Max is a hyperkinetic rabbity-thing with a taste for mayhem. Together, they''re a team of freelance police officers, on a mission to take down a bizarre mind-control conspiracy. Get ready to meet some off-kilter characters and to puzzle through some brain-tickling conundrums. Grab your Wii Remote, sit back on the sofa and get ready for some side-splitting humor!');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(166,74,'EN','Sam & Max: Season One','');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(167,74,'FR','Sam & Max: Saison 1','Nous vivons dans un monde impitoyable rempli de psychopathes. Heureusement que Sam & Max sont là pour s''occuper d''eux et ramener la paix, par la force si possible.
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(168,74,'DE','Sam & Max Season One','Das Humor-Upgrade für deine Wii! Arbeite mit Sam & Max, dem selbsternannten freiberuflichen Polizisten Duo, am Erreichen der kriminellen Gerechtigkeit zusammen. Enthülle Hinweise, verhöre Verdächtige, knacke sechs bizarre Fälle und finde selbst heraus warum Sam & Max zum witzigsten Spiele des Jahres gekürt wurde.');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(169,75,'EN','Rock Band Classic Rock Track Pack','Rock Band Track Pack: Classic Rock is a standalone software product that allows owners of Rock Band and Rock Band 2 to keep the party going with more hit songs from the pantheon of rock music. In addition, Rock Band Track Pack: Classic Rock, like all Rock Band software, is compatible with all Rock Band instrument controllers and other current music-based video game peripherals. The 20-song pack features an outstanding mix of Rock Band fans’ favorite classic rock hits including songs by mega artists The Who, Rush, Boston and Police. 
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(170,76,'EN','The Sims 2: Castaway','Help your Sims build a life from scratch after washing ashore on a deserted tropical island. Overcome the forces of nature to help them become the ultimate survivors and thrive in this undiscovered paradise while unearthing clues that will lead them back to civilization. Build shelters, craft unique items, and discover many useful treasures and ancient mysteries hidden deep within a diverse jungle environment filled with plants, fruits, and even wildlife. Your Sims change as they take on the challenges of island life and learn to survive in style. Create a new life for your Sims on an uncharted island in The Sims 2 Castaway. Choose from a wide range of Sims - Auto Mechanic, Chef, Doctor, Musician, Teacher, Executive, or Park Ranger. Each one brings a unique Sim humor and quirkiness to your crew. Reunite members of your crew and build a thriving community. ');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(171,77,'EN','Sims 2: Castaway','Help your Sims build a life from scratch after washing ashore on a deserted tropical island. Overcome the forces of nature to help them become the ultimate survivors and thrive in this undiscovered paradise while unearthing clues that will lead them back to civilization. Build shelters, craft unique items, and discover many useful treasures and ancient mysteries hidden deep within a diverse jungle environment filled with plants, fruits, and even wildlife. Your Sims change as they take on the challenges of island life and learn to survive in style. Create a new life for your Sims on an uncharted island in The Sims 2 Castaway. Choose from a wide range of Sims - Auto Mechanic, Chef, Doctor, Musician, Teacher, Executive, or Park Ranger. Each one brings a unique Sim humor and quirkiness to your crew. Reunite members of your crew and build a thriving community.');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(172,77,'FR','Les Sims 2: Naufragés','Les Sims 2 : Naufragés sur Wii est un titre de la célèbre franchise de simulation de vie virtuelle. Cette fois vos Sims sont dans une situation assez embêtante : ils se sont échoués sur une île déserte ! Assurez votre survie en vous aidant de tout ce qui vous tomber sous la main, ne devenez pas un sauvage et pensez à vous laver de temps en temps, entraidez-vous en découvrant de nouveaux rescapés qui peuvent vous filer un coup de main. Enfin, faites tout pour essayer de revenir à la civilisation.');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(173,77,'DE','Die Sims 2: Gestrandet','Im neuen Konsolenspiel Die Sims 2: Gestrandet erleben die Sims ihr größtes Abenteuer. Sie müssen sich ein neues Leben aufbauen, nachdem sie auf einer einsamen Insel gestrandet sind. Dort sind die Sims von Pflanzen, Bäumen, Früchten und auch wilden Tieren umgeben. Aber Achtung: Die idyllische Umgebung ist trügerisch, denn die Gestrandeten müssen absolut bei Null anfangen. Von den Grundbedürfnissen wie Essen und Trinken oder einem Dach über dem Kopf bis hin zum Herstellen von Werkzeug, Kleidung, Möbeln wird ihnen einiges an Mut und Können abverlangt. Es warten eine Vielzahl von Abenteuern und Herausforderungen auf die Sims, um die Naturgewalten zu überleben und die Insel lebbar zu machen. Auf der Suche nach Schätzen und mysteriösen Stätten gibt es versteckte Hinweise auf den Weg zurück in die Zivilisation. 
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(174,77,'IT','The Sims 2: Island','');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(175,77,'NL','De Sims 2 op een Onbewoond Eiland','');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(176,77,'PT','Os SIMS 2: Naufragos','Ajuda os teus Sims a reconstruir a vida do zero, depois de serem varridos para uma ilha deserta. Descobre uma ilha deserta e prepara-a para os Sims sobreviverem. Vais ter que os ajudar! Constrói abrigos e descobre imensos tesouros e mistérios que estão escondidos numa selva repleta de plantas, frutas e vida selvagem. Não te esqueças que os teus Sims ao longo do jogo vão evoluir e conseguir entrar em determinados desafios na ilha e aprender a sobreviver com estilo. Cria uma nova vida para os teus Sims em Os Sims™ 2 Náufragos');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(177,78,'EN','EA Sports Active: Personal trainer','Revolutionize your workout regimen with EA SPORTS Active, the ultimate interactive fitness program that''s designed for you. Get fit with a holistic approach to fitness that combines nutrition and lifestyle factors, with a variety of activities, all from the convenience of your living room. From customized routines that target upper body, lower body, and cardio to a guided 30-day challenge that tests muscle endurance, coordination and agility, stay in shape with fitness made fun and easy.');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(178,79,'EN','EA SPORTS Active Personal Trainer Wii 30-Hi Seikatsu Kaizen Program','');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(179,79,'JA','EA SPORTS アクティブ パーソナルトレーナー Wii -30日生活改善プログラム-','');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(180,79,'ZHTW',' 	EA SPORTS Active Personal Trainer Wii 30-Hi Seikatsu Kaizen Program (Japan Version) EA SPORTS Active Personal Trainer Wii 30日生活改善(日) ','本作是一款收錄了跑步、健走、棒球、網球、拳擊及舞蹈等各種運動項目的遊戲，從簡易到高階運動都包含在內，還有可以讓玩家30天內改善生活型態的“30日挑戰”課程，藉著搖桿及雙節棍的輔助，手腳並用，再搭配具有抗力的彈力繩及平衡板，讓玩家能更確實地體驗正確的動作。
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(181,80,'EN','EA Sports Active: Personal Trainer','');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(182,80,'FR','EA Sports Active','Développé en collaboration avec des experts du fitness dont Bob Greene (physiologiste de l’exercice, auteur et coach personnel d’Oprah Winfrey), EA SPORTS Active convient à toutes celles et ceux qui cherchent une façon simple, amusante et efficace de se maintenir en forme.
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(183,80,'DE','EA Sports Active','EA SPORTS Active wurde in Zusammenarbeit mit Fitnessexperten entwickelt und bietet unterhaltsame, leicht erlernbare Übungen und Aktivitäten, die zu einem westlich orientierten Fitnessprogramm für dich und deine Familie und Freunde kombiniert werden - und das komfortabel im Wohnzimmer. So hat man seinen eigenen Fitnesstrainer bequem zu Hause und kann zu mehr Wohlbefinden kommen.
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(184,80,'PT','EA Sports Active','Fitness Activo é Divertido e Fácil Os circuitos de 20 minutos incluem variedade e actividades familiares que se concentram no tronco, nas pernas, bem como cardio. Começa com uma corrida, seguida de exercícios para os bíceps e acelera os teus batimentos cardíacos com cardio de boxe. Fica em forma e diverte-te em apenas minutos por dia! Os Benefícios de um Treinador numa Caixa O teu treinador será o ponto central da experiência, orientando-te para a tua própria versão de realização pessoal. Serão oferecidos comentários ao longo de todo o exercício, mantendo-te concentrado no cumprimento dos teus objectivos de fitness. Desafio de 30 Dias O jogo acompanha o teu progresso enquanto cumpres o Desafio de 30 Dias e adequa os treinos de 20 minutos ao teu nível de fitness. Os circuitos mudam à medida que progrides todos os dias e o EA SPORTS Active controlará as calorias, intensidade e progreso ao longo de todo o percurso. Nova Maneira de Jogar Coloca o Nunchuk na correia de pernas especial e segura o Comando Remoto Wii na mão para controlares os movimentos do teu tronco e pernas. Também inclui uma banda de resistência para aumentar a intensidade de exercícios como o treino de bíceps e de ombros. Fica em Forma com os teus Amigos e Família Dois jogadores podem fazer exercício em conjunto enquanto as suas calorias e pontuações de treino são controladas individualmente. Utilizando ecrãs divididos, os dois podem fazer o seu treino personalizado e fazê-lo em conjunto. Exercício à Tua Maneira Os circuitos podem ser personalizados consoante o teu interesse e nível de fitness. Escolhe a tua duração, intensidade e define os teus próprios objectivos para calorias queimadas e pontuação de treino. Compatibilidade com o Wii Balance Board Tira mais partido do teu treino EA SPORTS Active com um Wii Balance Board, com mais funcionalidade e maiores benefícios físicos de muitos exercícios.');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(185,81,'EN','Suzumiya Haruhi no Heiretsu','');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(186,81,'JA','涼宮ハルヒの並列','小説にアニメにマンガやゲーム、さまざまに広がり続けるハルヒワールド。今度はWiiで、新たな舞台、新たなストーリーと共に登場！
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(187,81,'ZHTW','涼宮春日的並列(日)','遊戲以一艘豪華客輪為舞台，以全3D 的形式展現 SOS 團以及客輪風景。遊戲將在客輪這個封閉的空間中進行，而時間也設定為特殊的無線循環，每當迎來結局時都會進行時間倒流的「時間移動」，玩家可以在相同的時間軸中數次體驗不同的遊戲樂趣。 
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(188,82,'EN','Phantom Brave: We Meet Again','Released in 2004 Phantom Brave revolutionized the strategy RPG genre with its unique free roaming battle fields and a unit summoning system called "CONFINE". Now Phantom Brave returns to a new console with added features and extra chapter stories. Everything from the original game will be carried over, so gamers who haven''t played Phantom Brave can fully enjoy this title. The Story: A world of vast seas and small island continents, Ivoire existed in peace and harmony. Ancient mystic forces with forgotten powers now threaten the existence of man kind. Islands, once flourishing with life, now lie as empty waste lands. Remaining decadent cities are corrupted by unnatural events and violence. The shadow of darkness is slowly, but surely, engulfing the world of Ivoir. In the year of 921, in a world called Ivoire, lives Marona, a 13 year old orphaned girl with a special ability to communicate with phantoms. Her ability brings resentment from others, but cheerful and optimistic Marona is not bothered. Marona believes in her parents'' teachings that people will one day come to like her as long as she stays compassionate and kind. Now Marona travels throughout Ivoire with her guardian, Ash the Phantom, to resolve disputes around the world.');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(189,83,'EN','Phantom Brave Wii','');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(190,83,'JA','ファントム・ブレイブWii','いつでもどこでもやりたい放題！それが『ファントム・ブレイブ Wii』。
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(191,83,'ZHTW','通靈戰士(日)','《通靈戰士》(Phantom Brave)是一套由 Nippon Ichi Software  製作的角色扮演策略遊戲，它同時也是 Nippon Ichi Software(日本一Software) 在一年的時間裡製作的第三款 PS2 遊戲，有趣的是，這也是製作公司首次兼做發行。
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(192,84,'EN','ATV Quad Kings','Speed may earn you victories, but to wear the crown in ATV Quad Kings, you''ll need to show some style! Travel across the globe to compete in nine locations. Pick your four-wheeler from an array of quad bikes and dune buggys, each with different performance specs, then cash in your winnings to improve your ride. Rise to the top in four skill levels and master all the right moves in four game modes: World Tour, Arcade, Time Trial, and Freestyle. Being first to the finish in hard-fought races is good, but to be Number One you''ll need to catch air and perform some serious tricks in freestyle contests, too.');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(193,85,'EN','The Spiderwick Chronicles','Unlock and explore the hidden world of the seen and unseen from the Spiderwick Chronicles movie. Battle strange and enchanted creatures in this spellbound world of eerie adventures, as you fight to stop a rising evil.');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(194,86,'EN','The Spiderwick Chronicles','Unlock and explore the hidden world of the seen and unseen from the Spiderwick Chronicles movie. Battle strange and enchanted creatures in this spellbound world of eerie adventures, as you fight to stop a rising evil. ');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(195,86,'FR','Les Chroniques De Spiderwick','Pénétrez dans un autre monde et battez-vous pour arrêter une force démoniaque avant qu''elle ne devienne toute puissante dans les Chroniques de Spiderwick. Basé sur les célèbres livres et film du même nom, les Chroniques de Spiderwick sur Wii vous invite à tenir les rôles de Jared, Mallory et Simon Grace, des jumeaux et leur petite sœur, alors qu''ils explorent les terres de l''incroyable domaine de Spiderwick et essayent de protéger les recherches de leur grand-oncle Arthur.
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(196,86,'DE','Die Geheimnisse der Spiderwicks','Spannende Abenteuer und Rätsel erwarten dich im Spiderwick Universum! Die drei Geschwister Jared, Simon und Mallory ziehen mit ihrer Mutter in das schon etwas verfallene, geheimnisvoll anmutende Haus ihrer Großtante ein. Einst wohnte die Großtante mit ihrem Mann Arthur Spiderwick dort. Als Jared eines Tages auf Erkundungstour durch das Haus geht, entdeckt er in einem unbewohnten immer ein geheimnisvolles Buch. Ein handgeschriebener Brief warnt davor, das Buch zu öffnen, geschweige denn darin zu lesen. Doch Jared ist neugierig und ignoriert die Warnung. Es ist das Buch von Arthur Spiderwick, das Jared den Zutritt in eine unsichtbare Welt offenbart.
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(197,87,'EN','Donkey Kong: Jungle Beat','Swing through the jungle in DK’s craziest adventure ever! You’ll run, jump, backflip, and punch your way to greatness—now with new controls on Wii. You’ll use the buttons and Control Stick on the Wii Remote and Nunchuk controllers to move DK, and you’ll swing the Wii Remote controller to grab objects and clap with devastating power. When it comes time to box, you’ll punch with both hands! Explore one of the most imaginative worlds ever seen in a game, now with many areas partially redesigned to take full advantage of the new Wii controls. Newcomers will enjoy its fantastic jungles, dazzling caverns and wondrous seas for the first time, and fans of the original will discover new thrills along the way!');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(198,87,'ES','Donkey Kong Jungle Beat "New Play Control"','Nueva versión para Wii del juego de plataformas originalmente creado para GameCube, que cuenta con un control adaptado a wiimote y nunchuk, nuevos objetos, enemigos y dos nuevos niveles.
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(199,88,'EN','Donkey Kong: Jungle Beat','Swing through the jungle in DK’s craziest adventure ever! You’ll run, jump, backflip, and punch your way to greatness—now with new controls on Wii. You’ll use the buttons and Control Stick on the Wii Remote and Nunchuk controllers to move DK, and you’ll swing the Wii Remote controller to grab objects and clap with devastating power. When it comes time to box, you’ll punch with both hands! Explore one of the most imaginative worlds ever seen in a game, now with many areas partially redesigned to take full advantage of the new Wii controls. Newcomers will enjoy its fantastic jungles, dazzling caverns and wondrous seas for the first time, and fans of the original will discover new thrills along the way! ');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(200,88,'JA','Wiiであそぶ ドンキーコングジャングルビート','');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(201,88,'ZHTW','大金剛．叢林節奏(日)','本遊戲以與瑪俐歐同為任天堂元老級遊戲角色的 「大金剛（Donkey Kong）」為主角，遊戲並不採用傳統動作遊戲的搖桿或是十字鈕來操作，而是使用先前所推出，原本用於音樂節奏遊戲《大金剛鼓（Donkey Konga）》的專屬康加鼓控制器來操作。
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(202,89,'EN','Donkey Kong Jungle Beat','Swing through the jungle in DK’s craziest adventure ever! You’ll run, jump, backflip, and punch your way to greatness—now with new controls on Wii. You’ll use the buttons and Control Stick on the Wii Remote and Nunchuk controllers to move DK, and you’ll swing the Wii Remote controller to grab objects and clap with devastating power. When it comes time to box, you’ll punch with both hands! Explore one of the most imaginative worlds ever seen in a game, now with many areas partially redesigned to take full advantage of the new Wii controls. Newcomers will enjoy its fantastic jungles, dazzling caverns and wondrous seas for the first time, and fans of the original will discover new thrills along the way! ');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(203,89,'FR','Nouvelle Façon de Jouer: Donkey Kong Jungle Beat','Le roi de la jungle est de retour et il va faire le singe sur Wii! Donkey Kong Jungle Beat NOUVELLE FAÇON DE JOUER! vous permet de redécouvrir ce grand succès GameCube sur Wii: nouvelles commandes, niveaux repensés, nouveaux ennemis et modes de jeu supplémentaires pour votre plus grand plaisir.
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(204,89,'DE','Donkey Kong Jungle Beat (NPC)','Voll Banane! Donkey Kong ist zurück. Der sympathische Pixel-Primat mischt jetzt die Wii auf und erobert sich im nu neue Fans. NEW PLAY CONTROL! Donkey Kong Jungle Beat ist eine neue Version des klassischen GameCube-Abenteuers Donkey Kong.
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(205,89,'NL','Donkey Kong Jungle Beat','De koning van de jungle is terug, en hij zet iedereen voor aap op de Wii! NEW PLAY CONTROL! Donkey Kong Jungle Beat brengt de unieke GameCube-hit in topvorm naar de Wii, inclusief een geheel nieuwe bewegingsgevoelige besturing, nieuwe levelontwerpen, verse vijanden en een beste tros extra spelvarianten.
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(206,90,'EN','SimAnimals','SimAnimals, take the wild world of animals into your hands. Embrace all the adventure, fun, and mischief that await you in the vast forest. Feed a bear what he craves. Pick up a rabbit or hedgehog, and bring him to his friends. Discover what other creatures lurk in the wild. You have the power to reach out and touch, pick up and move everything in the forest from squirrels and foxes to trees and flowers. Make your wild animals happy and maintain a forest that lets them flourish as you venture further into the forest than you''ve ever been before. Engage wild animals, experience life in the forest, and let your creativity run wild in SimAnimals.');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(207,91,'EN','Sim Animals','');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(208,91,'JA','シムアニマル','『シムシティ』の生みの親、ウィル・ライトが制作した『ザ・シムズ』シリーズがWiiに登場！豊かな自然に恵まれた森には、たくさんの動物が暮らしています。動物とふれあいながら、森のみんなを幸せにしてあげてください。森の奥深くには楽しい冒険が待っています。森の生物がハッピーでいられるように森をきれいに保ち、彼等の繁栄を助けましょう。さらに、育てた森に住む動物や植物にふれることも可能！おなかをすかせたクマにご飯をあげたり、ウサギやはりねずみを掴んで友達のところに連れて行ってあげたり…。あなたの想像力で森がどんどん大きくなっていきます。さあ、『シムアニマル』で、初めて見る森への旅に出かけましょう。 ');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(209,91,'ZHTW','模擬動物(日)','玩家在叢林的冒險過程中，將聽到許多交織成遊戲配樂的音樂片段。每個地方，一開始都有獨特的樂曲，包括古老城堡遺蹟的凱爾特音樂，以及老舊廢物堆積場的古怪旋律。此外，遊戲會以獨奏管絃樂器的簡短旋律強調動物生活中的重大事件，還會以大規模管絃樂章闡釋玩家在世界中所做的抉擇。
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(210,92,'EN','Sim Animals','');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(211,92,'FR','SimAnimals','Avec SimAnimals, le tout dernier opus de la fameuse franchise des jeux Sims, entrez littéralement en contact avec la nature !
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(212,92,'DE','Sim Animals','Der speziell für Nintendo Wii und DS entwickelte Titel lässt den Spieler aktiv in die Tierwelt eintauchen und die wilden Tiere in ihrer natürlichen Umgebung erkunden. Mit Hilfe einer animierten Hand interagiert der Spieler mit Tieren und Pflanzen. Ziel ist es, im Tierreich Beziehungen einzugehen, beim Aufbau einer Familie zu helfen und gemeinsam die Herausforderungen der Wildnis zu meistern. 
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(213,93,'EN','Championship Foosball','Jump into the fast-paced action and fun of foosball in your own living room! Using motion-sensing technology in the Wii Remote, Championship Foosball creates a realistic gaming experience so you will feel like you are playing at a real table! Create your own team of players and choose to play using official foosball rules or create custom rules to suit your game. Challenge your friends in 4-player action or rise throughout the ranks in single-player mode and play on a host of official tables designed in partnership with the International Table Soccer Federation.');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(214,94,'EN','Table Football','Table Football uses the motion-sensing technology in the Wii remote to create a realistic feeling table football game – players will feel like they are actually playing at a real foosball table!
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(215,94,'FR','Baby Foot','Grâce à votre Wii, retrouvez toutes les sensations du hobby de bistrot avec Baby Foot. Utilisez la Wiimote et le Nunchuck comme barres et faites tournicoter vos petits joueurs virtuels afin de marquer des buts. A vous les roulettes et autres règles fantaisistes. Jouez en multi avec la possibilité de personnaliser entièrement vos parties.');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(216,94,'DE','Tischfußball 2008',' Endlich hält die beliebteste Sportart Einzug in jedes Wohnzimmer: passend zur EM veröffentlicht THQ Tischfußball 2008 exklusiv für die Wii! Dank der revolutionären Steuerung über die Wii Remote können Sie im Handumdrehen ins Spiel einsteigen!
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(217,94,'IT','Calcio Balilla','');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(218,95,'EN','SimCity Creator','Be a powerful mayor and build your ultimate city—constructing homes, businesses, factories, skyscrapers, freeways, railroads, and much more. Try different city styles, including American, European, Asian, Futuristic and many others. Hire assistants and advisors with unique personalities to help you manage your town and build new neighborhoods. When you want to check out what you’ve built, fly over it in your plane to see all the detail of your design. If you want to give your city a little excitement, send in a giant monster or set off an earthquake to wreck it—you built it, you can destroy it. The fate of your city and your citizens is in your hands!');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(219,96,'EN','Simcity Creator','');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(220,96,'JA','シムシティ クリエイター','都市育成シミュレーション『シムシティ』がＷｉｉに登場！
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(221,96,'ZHTW','模擬城市．建築師(日)','玩家要成為極富權力的市長，創造、欣賞及摧毀你的終極城市。從為城市劃分區域開始，建設住宅、商業建築、工廠、 摩天大樓、高速公路、 鐵路等等。透過專為Wii 和 Wii遙控器設計的嶄新使用者介面，玩家將發現各種自行改造城市的方法，包括 13 種城市風格等著你去探索，例如美國、歐洲和亞洲主題等等。
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(222,97,'EN','SimCity Creator','');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(223,97,'KO','심시티 나만의 도시','');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(224,98,'EN','Simcity Creator','');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(225,98,'FR','Simcity Creator','SimCity Creator sur Wii vous propose de créer votre propre ville en la personnalisant à votre guise. Il est possible de faire en sorte que la ville soit typée américaine, européenne ou encore futuriste. En tant que maire, il ne tient qu''à vous d''en faire une ville prospère où il fait bon vivre. Si la tâche devient laborieuse, vous pouvez toujours lancer une attaque de monstre sur votre cité et tout démolir !');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(226,98,'DE','Simcity Creator','Baue faszinierende Städte, spiele mit ihnen und stifte Chaos mit SimCity Creator für Wii! 
