INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(262,115,'ZHTW','零 月蝕之假面(日)','遊戲故事敘述水無月流歌等 5 名少女小時候曾一同遭到綁架，最後被某位刑警平安救出。在綁架事件數年後，5 名少女中已有 2 人死亡，殘存的海咲與圓香則是一同前往案發地點朧月島。為了明白當年事件的真相，流歌也跟著前往神秘的朧月島一探究竟。
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(263,116,'EN','Neopets Puzzle Adventure','Neopets Puzzle Adventure offers an in-depth and exciting storyline full of puzzle-based gameplay set in the world of Neopets. The game offers pick up and play gameplay, new never-before-seen areas in the Neopets universe to explore, and the opportunity to redeem codes for exclusive virtual items at the Neopets website. The game board itself resembles a chessboard, while the gameplay takes the principles of Reversi and Go, and adds new twists that take the adventure to unexpected levels. The goal is to turn all of the chips on the board to your Neopet''s color.
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(264,117,'EN','Neopets Puzzle Adventure','Neopets Puzzle Adventure offers an in-depth and exciting storyline full of puzzle-based gameplay set in the world of Neopets. The game offers pick up and play gameplay, new never-before-seen areas in the Neopets universe to explore, and the opportunity to redeem codes for exclusive virtual items at the Neopets website. The game board itself resembles a chessboard, while the gameplay takes the principles of Reversi and Go, and adds new twists that take the adventure to unexpected levels. The goal is to turn all of the chips on the board to your Neopet''s color.
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(265,117,'DE','Neopets Puzzle Adventure','Die Welt der Neopets öffnet ihre Tore. Gemeinsam mit Nickelodeon und Infinite Interactive, den Entwicklern von "Puzzle Quest", veröffentlicht Capcom für Nintendo den Multiplattformtitel Neopets Puzzle Adventure. In Anlehnung an die klassischen Brettspiele Reversi und Go - kombiniert mit spaßigen Minispielen und echtem Neopets-Flair - machen die Comic-Kreaturen Lust auf knifflige Knobelpartien. 
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(266,118,'EN','Qui Veut Gagner Des Millions: 1ère Edition','');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(267,118,'FR','Qui Veut Gagner Des Millions: 1ère Edition','Retrouvez sur Wii le célèbre jeu présenté par Jean-Pierre Foucault. Qui Veut Gagner des Millions? vous place en tête-à-tête avec votre culture générale et vos (mé)connaissances. A vous d''escalader la pyramide des gains et d''utiliser vos jokers à bon escient pour décrocher le pactole. Retrouvez l''ambiance de l''émission télé avec son animateur vedette vous posant les questions qui fâchent.');
