INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(311,136,'EN','Harry Potter and the Order of the Phoenix','The close and synergistic relationship between book, film and videogame is more defined in the Harry Potter and the Order of the Phoenix videogame than ever before. Players will be able to explore the many key locations within Hogwarts in minute detail, each one a visual match to its film equivalent, while being engrossed in the thrilling adventures outlined in the rich narrative of the book. 
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(312,136,'FR','Harry Potter et l''Ordre du Phénix','Pour la première fois, les joueurs vont ressentir toute la magie d''Harry Potter en maniant la télécommande Wii comme une baguette magique ! Lancez des sorts d''un simple mouvement de poignet et aidez Harry à lever le voile sur de ténébreux secrets dans Harry Potter et l''Ordre du Phénix.
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(313,136,'DE',' Wii Harry Potter und der Orden des Phönix','Mit der Wii-Fernbedienung als Zauberstab kannst du jetzt erstmals den Zauber von Harry Potter am eigenen Leib erfahren! Zaubere mit einer einfachen Handbewegung und hilf Harry Potter dabei, die dunklen Geheimnisse in Harry Potter und der Orden des Phönix zu enthüllen.
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(314,136,'ES','Harry Potter Y La Orden Del Fenix','');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(315,136,'IT','Harry Potter e l''Ordine della Fenice','');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(316,136,'NL','Harry Potter en de Orde van de Feniks','');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(317,136,'PT','Harry Potter e a Ordem da Fénix','Harry Potter e a Ordem de Fénix™ conta-nos a história de Harry no regresso a Hogwarts para o seu quinto ano de estudos. Surpreendentemente o jovem descobre que a maior parte da comunidade de feiticeiros se recusa a reconhecer o seu recente encontro com Lord Voldemort, preferindo ignorar que Voldemort voltou. Com toda a comunidade de feiticeiros ameaçada e os alunos mal preparados para se defenderem das forças das trevas, Hermione e Ron pedem a ajuda de Harry para resolver o problema. Um pequeno grupo de alunos que se intitulam “O Exército de Dumbledore” começam a encontrar-se em segredo onde Harry os vai ensinar e prepará-los para a extraordinária batalha. Com a capacidade de jogar várias personagens, incluindo Harry Potter, Dumbledore e Sirius Black, Harry Potter e a Ordem de Fénix™ oferece aos jogadores a oportunidade de empunharem uma varinha, explorar Hogwarts e viver uma das histórias mais emocionantes e perigosas da vida de Harry Potter.');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(318,137,'EN','Harry Potter and the Order of the Phoenix','');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(319,137,'FR','Harry Potter et l''Ordre du Phénix','Pour la première fois, les joueurs vont ressentir toute la magie d''Harry Potter en maniant la télécommande Wii comme une baguette magique ! Lancez des sorts d''un simple mouvement de poignet et aidez Harry à lever le voile sur de ténébreux secrets dans Harry Potter et l''Ordre du Phénix.
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(320,137,'DE','Harry Potter und der Orden des Phönix','In Harry Potter und der Orden des Phönix tritt Harry sein fünftes Jahr in Hogwarts an und muss feststellen, dass der größte Teil der Zauberergemeinschaft die Wahrheit über seine letzte Begegnung mit Lord Voldemort nicht kennt. Aus Angst, der ehrwürdige Schulleiter von Hogwarts, Albus Dumbledore, könne ihn diskreditieren und sein Amt übernehmen, ernennt der Minister für Zauberei, Cornelius Fudge, eine neue Lehrerin für Verteidigung gegen die dunklen Künste, die Dumbledore und die Hogwarts-Schüler im Auge behalten soll. 
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(321,137,'IT','Harry Potter e l''Ordine della Fenice','');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(322,137,'PT','Harry Potter e a Ordem da Fénix','Harry Potter e a Ordem de Fénix™ conta-nos a história de Harry no regresso a Hogwarts para o seu quinto ano de estudos. Surpreendentemente o jovem descobre que a maior parte da comunidade de feiticeiros se recusa a reconhecer o seu recente encontro com Lord Voldemort, preferindo ignorar que Voldemort voltou. Com toda a comunidade de feiticeiros ameaçada e os alunos mal preparados para se defenderem das forças das trevas, Hermione e Ron pedem a ajuda de Harry para resolver o problema. Um pequeno grupo de alunos que se intitulam “O Exército de Dumbledore” começam a encontrar-se em segredo onde Harry os vai ensinar e prepará-los para a extraordinária batalha. Com a capacidade de jogar várias personagens, incluindo Harry Potter, Dumbledore e Sirius Black, Harry Potter e a Ordem de Fénix™ oferece aos jogadores a oportunidade de empunharem uma varinha, explorar Hogwarts e viver uma das histórias mais emocionantes e perigosas da vida de Harry Potter.');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(323,138,'EN','Mortimer Beckett and the Secrets of Spooky Manor','In "Mortimer Beckett and the Secrets of Spooky Manor" for the Wii, players will hunt the halls of Spooky Manor for hidden objects, return the items to their rightful places and solve a series of brain-bending puzzles to get to the bottom of this eerie mystery. Only those with a keen eye for detail will discover the answers hidden in Spooky Manor. When playing Mortimer Beckett on Wii, players are fully immersed in the game play experience as they point the Wii RemoteTM at items on the screen or shake it to get rid of pesky ghosts. And with the options of single player, head-to-head or co-operative modes, there''s always seek and find fun waiting for the whole family, right in the comfort of your own living room.');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(324,139,'EN','Mortimer Beckett and The Secrets of Spooky Manor','');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(325,140,'EN','Grand Slam Tennis','Developed specifically for the Wii, EA SPORTS Grand Slam Tennis delivers the deepest and richest tennis experience ever developed for the platform with real life tennis strokes letting anyone quickly pick up a racket and use every shot type and inch of the court. It is the exclusive home of Wimbledon and includes all four Grand Slams: the Australian Open, Roland Garros, the U.S. Open and Wimbledon. The player line-up features some of the greatest and most accomplished ever including John McEnroe in his exclusive video game debut. Joining Mac is an impressive roster of current and legendary men''s and women''s players who collectively own 135 Grand Slam singles titles, making this the most accomplished group of players ever assembled for a tennis video game.');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(326,141,'EN','Grand Slam Tennis','');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(327,141,'JA','グランドスラムテニス','');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(328,141,'ZHTW','大滿貫網球(日)','《大滿貫網球》的Wii遊戲，本作將對應Wii的最新周邊MotionPlus，玩家揮動球拍的動作要求更加的精準。
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(329,142,'EN','Grand Slam Tennis','Developed specifically for the Wii, EA SPORTS Grand Slam Tennis delivers the deepest and richest tennis experience ever developed for the platform with real life tennis strokes letting anyone quickly pick up a racket and use every shot type and inch of the court. It is the exclusive home of Wimbledon and includes all four Grand Slams: the Australian Open, Roland Garros, the U.S. Open and Wimbledon. The player line-up features some of the greatest and most accomplished ever including John McEnroe in his exclusive video game debut. Joining Mac is an impressive roster of current and legendary men''s and women''s players who collectively own 135 Grand Slam singles titles, making this the most accomplished group of players ever assembled for a tennis video game.');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(330,142,'FR','Grand Chelem Tennis','Jeu, set et match! Le premier jeu de tennis signé EA Sports débarque sur Wii. EA SPORTS Grand Chelem Tennis vous offre une expérience de jeu passionnante soutenue par un réalisme inégalé. 23 légendes du tennis, dont Roger Federer, John McEnroe, Boris Becker et Serena Williams, s''affrontent pour décrocher le titre ultime et réussir le Grand Chelem. 
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(331,142,'DE','Grand Slam Tennis','EA SPORTS™ heißt ein neues Mitglied in seiner Familie der Weltklasse-Spielereihen willkommen. EA SPORTS Grand Slam® Tennis bietet mit authentischen Tennisbewegungen auf den berühmtesten Courts der Welt das umfassendste und mitreißendste Tenniserlebnis, das jemals für Wii™ entwickelt wurde. Im Profitennis geht es vor allem um die Grand Slam-Turniere, und EAs neues Tennisspiel macht hier keine Ausnahme. 
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(332,142,'ES','Grand Slam Tennis','EA Sports ofrece a los usuarios de Nintendo Wii la posibilidad de ganar los cuatro torneos por excelencia del tenis en la piel de los jugadores más emblemáticos del circuito.
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(333,143,'EN','Guilty Gear XX','');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(334,143,'FR','Guilty Gear XX Accent Core','Guilty Gear XX Accent Core est un jeu de combat en 2D sur Wii. Le titre propose plus d''une vingtaine de personnages différents dont deux nouveaux (Order Sol et A.B.A.) par rapport au volet précédant. Affrontez vos ennemis à coups de combos dévastateurs, en dirigeant des persos tous plus originaux les uns que les autres.');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(335,144,'EN','Wii Music','When it comes to music and rhythm games, Wii Music stands in a class of its own. Unlike other music games, which penalize players if they don''t play perfectly, Wii Music is a musical playground where there are no mistakes. Here anyone can pick up and master the huge array of instruments available, through simple motions like strumming and drumming. Musicians in your band jam by simply playing their instruments to the beat of a song or by improvising to their heart''s content. Play faster. Play slower. Skip a beat, or throw in 10 more. No matter what you do, Wii Music automatically transforms your improv stylings into great music.');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(336,145,'EN','Wii Music','');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(337,145,'JA','Wii Music(Wiiミュージック)','');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(338,145,'ZHTW','Wii 音樂(日)','最多可以有四人同時共同演奏音樂，利用獨特的Wii體感設計，可以模擬木琴、吉他、鈴、鼓、喇叭等樂器以接近真實的方式控制。當然，節奏的快慢則是由指揮來控制的。
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(339,146,'EN','Wii Music','Beyond the Jam 
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(340,146,'FR','Wii Music','Wii Music sur Wii amène une autre dimension au phénomène bien connu du Air Guitar. Ici, c''est par l''intermédiaire de votre Wiimote que vous allez faire semblant de jouer plus d''une soixantaine d''instruments, de la batterie au piano, du banjo à la cithare, du vibraphone au marimba. Le jeu se charge de retranscrire vos gesticulations en musique, pour des jam sessions d''anthologie.');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(341,146,'DE','Wii Music','Machen Sie Musik auf der Wii! 
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(342,146,'IT','Wii Music','Suona tanti classici senza tempo!
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(343,147,'EN','Go Play City Sports','When you''re a kid in the city, pavement is grass, the street''s your front yard, and parked cars are your picket fence. Go Play: City Sports captures the magic of playing games in the streets, using the Wii motion controls to re-create six favorite city sports. Stake your claim as king of the block in Kickball, Stickball, Jump Rope, Handball, Rooftop Hockey, and Shootout Soccer. Invite up to four friends to play on a team or go head-to-head, or explore the neighborhood in the single-player environment. The realism doesn''t stop with the motions, you''ll need to dodge obstacles like manholes, hydrants and parked cars while you play!');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(344,148,'EN','DiRT 2','Following on the success of the original Dirt as well as a decade of videogame development in partnership with the late Colin McRae, DiRT 2 explores various disciplines of off-road racing. DiRT 2 features a roster of contemporary off-road events, taking players to the most diverse and challenging real-world environments. This World Tour has players competing in aggressive multi-car and intense solo races at extraordinary new locations, from canyon racing and jungle trails to city stadium-based events. ');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(345,148,'ES','DiRT 2','Tras el éxito del Dirt original, así como una década de desarrollo del videojuego en asociación con el ultimo Colin McRae, DIRT 2 explota las diferentes disciplinas de carreras off-road. DiRT 2 ofrece una lista de los acontecimientos off-road, llevando a los jugadores a los más diversos ambientes del desafiante mundo real. Su gira mundial hace que jugadores compitan en agresivas carreras multiplayer o en solitario en extraordinarias nuevas localizaciones, desde las carreras del cañón y senderos de la selva, al estadio de la ciudad.');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(346,149,'EN','Colin McRae: DiRT 2','');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(347,149,'FR','Colin McRae: DiRT 2','Inspiré par les meilleures épreuves de course tout-terrain et de sports extrêmes, Dirt 2 vous propose un fabuleux tour du monde avec des épeuves classiques ou innovantes, de la Malaisie au Maroc en passant par Londres et L.A.
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(348,149,'DE','Colin McRae: DiRT 2','Colin McRae: DiRT 2 entführt den Spieler auf eine Welttournee voll aufregender Offroad-Events an spannenden, echten Orten. Colin McRae: DiRT 2 wurde von Grund auf an die Eigenheiten der Wii angepasst und bietet Plattform-exklusive, individuelle Strecken, Disziplinen und Features. Auf den Spieler warten in der DiRT 2 World Tour sechs Renndisziplinen mit den abwechslungsreichsten Offroad-Strecken der Welt, darunter herausfordernde Rallye-Wettbewerbe auf verschneiten Kursen, packende Wüsten-Raids oder frenetisch bejubelte Stadien-Rennen.
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(349,150,'EN','de Blob','The evil I.N.K.T. Corporation has declared ''Color is a Crime!'' and leeched Chroma City of all its beauty and interest. The race to rescue Chroma City has just begun, and only de Blob can save the world from a black-and-white future with his unique abilities to color the world back to life.');
