INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(431,191,'ZHTW','飛標 Wii DX(日)','本作正如其名，是一款以射飛鏢運動為主題的動作遊戲，玩家在遊戲裡可以把Wii搖桿當成飛鏢一樣來操作，並利用按下壓住「A」鈕來揮動搖桿將飛鏢射出，並以獲得畫面上顯示的鏢靶高分為目標來過關。而在遊戲規則方面，除了一般常見的加分玩法「Count-Up」之外、還有「Cricket」、「Zero 1」、「Rotation」、「CutThroat」等合計五種常見玩法，而且本作也支援最多四人同時對戰，玩家還可以透過任天堂Wi-Fi Connection將自己各遊戲的分數上傳到網路排行榜上去跟其他玩家們競賽唷！');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(432,192,'EN','Pop''n Music','');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(433,192,'JA','ポップンミュージック','');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(434,192,'ZHTW','流行節奏(日)','本作為Konami公司音樂遊戲商標「Bemani」的第二款遊戲作品，同時也是自1998年推出系列第一作以來就一直非常受到歡迎喜愛的人氣音樂遊戲「動感音樂」系列最新作品，在遊戲中，會有許多「動感君」不斷從畫面上方配合音樂節奏掉落下來，玩家必須依照各個動感君對應的九個按鈕鍵盤來看準時間按下按鈕，藉此來體驗有如音樂演奏一般的表演樂趣。
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(435,193,'EN','Harvest Moon: Tree Of Tranquility','You have moved to an island town that was once brimming with life and energy.… Now, however, the island is in trouble! The mystical Mother Tree that once watched over the island has disappeared, and the Harvest Goddess is nowhere to be found! The island has lost its connection with nature and the inhabitants don’t know what to do. It is up to you to save the island! Till the earth, befriend and raise animals, nurture friendships, and build a family. When the giant Mother Tree is reborn, the Harvest Goddess will be able to return and bring prosperity to the island once again. Harvest Moon: Tree of Tranquility is filled with exciting features that are sure to delight both new players and long-time Harvest Moon fans! There are lot of crops to grow, a variety of animals to care for, tons of festivals to participate in, and an exciting story!');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(436,194,'EN','Bokujo for Wii','');
