INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(515,226,'FR','The Beatles : Rock Band','The Beatles : Rock Band sur Wii est un jeu de rythme qui tire parti d''une sélection d''accessoires musicaux : guitare, basse, batterie et micro modelés pour correspondre au matériel utilisé par le célèbre groupe britannique. Le jeu comprend 45 morceaux issus du répertoire 1962-1969 des Beatles et propose même des compositions inédites.
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(516,226,'ES','The Beatles: Rock Band','¿Es la quincuagésima vez que te sientas a ver A hard days night? ¿Sigues tarereando Love me do en la ducha? ¿Crees que Come together es un tema tan moderno como cualquiera de los que suenan en la radio? ¿Tienes en tu cuarto una plaquita que tu hermana te trajo de The Cavern? Si has respondido afirmativamente a estas preguntas no necesitas un médico que te diagnostique: eres un beatlemaníaco.
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(517,227,'EN','Groovin'' Blocks','The blocks are droppin'', and you''ll be groovin'' and boppin'' in this musical puzzler that takes a catchy premise and makes it even catchier. Groovin'' Blocks starts a song and asks you to play along. As blocks fall from the top of the screen, arrange them by color at the bottom. You''ll clear space by successfully grouping blocks. But you''ll get bonus points if you move them in time to the music. Each level lasts for one song (assuming you make it that long). The game''s 27 stages are designed for all skill levels, and they''re all available from the start, so anyone can jump right into their favorite kind of groove.');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(518,228,'EN','Summer Athletics 2009','');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(519,228,'DE','Summer Athletics 2009','Auf die Plätze, fertig, los! 
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(520,229,'EN','Tiger Woods PGA Tour 10','Feel the drama of playing tournament golf with Tiger Woods PGA TOUR 10. For the first time in franchise history, take aim at capturing the U.S. Open Championship on the ever-challenging Bethpage Black. Playing in front of huge galleries and hearing crowd reactions from nearby holes, take your game to the next level when it matters most as you try to hold off a charging Tiger Woods and other PGA TOUR Pros. Whether you''re fighting the course, the crowd, dynamic weather conditions, or the field, feel the drama on every swing with Tiger Woods PGA TOUR 10.');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(521,230,'EN','Tiger Woods PGA Tour 10','Feel the drama of playing tournament golf with Tiger Woods PGA TOUR 10. For the first time in franchise history, take aim at capturing the U.S. Open Championship on the ever-challenging Bethpage Black. Playing in front of huge galleries and hearing crowd reactions from nearby holes, take your game to the next level when it matters most as you try to hold off a charging Tiger Woods and other PGA TOUR Pros. Whether you''re fighting the course, the crowd, dynamic weather conditions, or the field, feel the drama on every swing with Tiger Woods PGA TOUR 10.');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(522,230,'KO','타이거 우즈 PGA 투어 10','타이거 우즈 PGA Tour 시리즈가 새로운 요소를 추가하여 새롭게 등장하였습니다. 플레이어가 Wii 리모컨을 골프 클럽을 쥐듯이 잡고 플레이를 하면, 플레이어의 스윙에 따라 타이거 우즈 등 실제 프로 골프 선수들이 TV화면 속에서 스윙합니다. 오직 백스윙의 길이에 의해 퍼팅이 결정되는 기존의 「클래식 퍼팅」뿐 아니라 타이거 우즈 PGA Tour 10에는 백스윙의 길이와 스윙의 속도가 동시에 퍼팅의 세기를 결정하는 「정밀 퍼팅」이 추가되어 실제 상황과 비슷한 느낌으로 즐길 수 있습니다. 또한, 닌텐도 Wi-Fi 커넥션을 이용해 인터넷에 연결하면 온라인 모드로 세계 각국의 플레이어들과 라운드를 돌며 실력을 경쟁할 수 있습니다.
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(523,231,'EN','Tiger Woods PGA Tour 10','Feel the drama of playing tournament golf with Tiger Woods PGA TOUR 10. For the first time in franchise history, take aim at capturing the U.S. Open Championship on the ever-challenging Bethpage Black. Playing in front of huge galleries and hearing crowd reactions from nearby holes, take your game to the next level when it matters most as you try to hold off a charging Tiger Woods and other PGA TOUR Pros.Whether you''re fighting the course, the crowd, dynamic weather conditions, or the field, feel the drama on every swing with Tiger Woods PGA TOUR 10.');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(524,231,'FR','Tiger Woods PGA Tour 10','Placez-vous sur l''aire de départ car Tiger Woods PGA TOUR® 10 débarque sur Wii et la simulation de golf entre dans une nouvelle ère: détection de mouvements révolutionnaire, présentation digne d''une vraie retransmission sportive, possibilité de participer à l''US Open pour la première fois dans l''histoire de la franchise. Tiger Woods PGA TOUR® 10 bénéficie d''un réalisme sans précédent et vous fait vivre les sensations d''un golfeur pro dans votre salon!
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(525,231,'DE','Tiger Woods PGA Tour 10','Erlebe in Tiger Woods PGA TOUR 10 Turniergolf in seiner ganzen Dramatik. Zum ersten Mal in der Franchise-Geschichte kannst du nun dein Können bei den fesselnden U.S. Open Championship auf dem anspruchsvollen Bethpage Black unter Beweis stellen. Wachse im entscheidenden Moment über dich hinaus und verweise Tiger Woods und die anderen PGA TOUR-Profis auf die Plätze. Zeig allen, dass Platzverhältnisse, Publikum, Wetter oder Gegner dich nicht stoppen können - und feiere dramatische Triumphe in Tiger Woods PGA TOUR 10. 
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(526,231,'NL','Tiger Woods PGA Tour 10','Bereid je voor om af te slaan, want Tiger Woods PGA TOUR 10 komt naar de Wii en staat op het punt je verwachtingen van golfsimulaties naar een nieuw niveau te tillen. Tiger Woods PGA Tour 10 combineert een revolutionaire swing-beweging met de authentieke presentatie van een sportuitzending en de kans om voor het eerst in de serie mee te doen aan de US Open, en brengt ongeëvenaard realisme en alle spanning van de Pro Tour direct bij je thuis.
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(527,232,'EN','Dance Party Pop Hits','Come and Join the Dance Party!
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(528,233,'EN','Sudoku Ball - Detective','Sudoku Ball Detective is Sudoku with a twist: play your favorite puzzle game in a completely new, entertaining detective scenario, and experience multitudes of challenging puzzles to solve a mysterious crime! An exclusive Sudoku ball design adds even more to your Sudoku experience.
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(529,233,'FR','Sudoku Ball - Detective','Inspiré du fameux jeu de société Cluedo et des célèbres enquêtes policières de Sherlock Holmes, Agatha Christie et Midsomer Murders, Sudoku Ball - Detective met le joueur à la place du détective d''une petite bourgade où un meurtre a été commis.
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(530,233,'DE','Sudoku Ball - Detective','Egal ob im motivierenden Einzelspielermodus, in dem der Spieler nicht nur die Sudoko-Rätsel lösen muss, sondern ganz nebenbei auch noch einen Mord aufklärt, oder in den anderen Spielmodi: Das neue und absolut einzigartige Sudoko-Ball-Feature, bei dem 6 Sudoko-Felder auf einem 3D-Ball miteinander verbunden sind, frischt das weltweit bekannte Sudoko-Gameplay ungemein auf und sorgt für ein komplett neues Sudoko-Feeling! 
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(531,234,'EN','Tiger Woods PGA Tour 09 All-Play','Whether you''re a seasoned veteran or hitting the links for the first time, now everybody swings on an even playing field, in Tiger Woods PGA Tour 09. Your career begins under the watchful eye of Hank Haney, Tiger Woods'' real-life coach, who takes you under his wing, helps you tune your clubs, and provides training drills to help improve your game. With experience under your belt and confidence as your ally, take aim at family, friends, and rivals in fun and challenging game modes, including the new Golf Party mini-game mode. With improved swing mechanics, an all-new controller system, and tutelage from one of the game''s best coaches, play your way to the top of the leader board with Tiger Woods PGA Tour 09. All new swing controls provides a one to one relationship between what you''re doing with the Wii remote and what your player is doing on screen, for the ultimate control and accuracy with every swing. For the first time on the Nintendo Wii, compete with a live foursome in the time it takes to play a single-player round.');
