INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(538,237,'FR','Tiger Woods PGA Tour 09 All-Play','Le plus célèbre des golfeurs s''illustre dans Tiger Woods PGA Tour 09 All-Play sur Wii. Le coach personnel de Tiger Woods (Hank Hankey) vous donnera des précieux conseils tout au long du jeu. Cet opus s''est attardé sur la progression du joueur avec un système qui s''adapte à tous les niveaux.');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(539,238,'EN','Cabela''s Outdoor Adventures 2010','Take on the challenges of the best hunting and fishing hot spots in North America! You''ll be tracking record-breaking big game, as well as small game, birds, and trophy fish. Real-life scenarios will keep your adrenaline pumping as you search for your prey. Advanced AI means the animals will react just how they would in the wild. But your realistic equipment and gear will make sure you have the edge you need to take down your prize! Integrated tutorials make sure everyone will have a chance. You can even design your own dream trophy buck, down to its size, color, and rack!');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(540,239,'EN','Arcade Zone','Once upon a time, when arcades were the hottest spots for gaming, having an arcade at home was a dream. Well, arcade fans, the dream comes true with this collection of favorites for Wii! Arcade Zone brings together classics and new hits to create a gaming paradise. Go retro and try your hand at Skee Ball and Whack-a-Mole, or wrestle with the claw machine. Flash your skills in newer favorites like Cyclone, Colorama, Spin-n-Win, and more. Play in five environments, each with a resident arcade hotshot and retro video game. Score big to win tickets that you can trade for everything from oversized stuffed animals to Chinese finger traps. ');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(541,240,'EN','Major League Baseball 2K9','Major League Baseball 2K9 captures animations such as batting stances, pitching windups, and signature swings. Game play enhancements include pitching, batting, fielding, and base running are user-friendly and enjoyable for both rookies and veterans. Major League Baseball 2K9 includes new commentary and presentation features.');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(542,241,'EN','Major League Baseball 2K9','');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(543,242,'EN','Balloon Pop','The infamous balloon thief has stolen the Earth''s precious season and sealed them away in his magical balloons. It is up to you to release the magic stored inside and bring life back to your planet one season at a time! With this revolutionary puzzle game that''s fit for all ages, players point at the screen to aim and link a series of balloons to create satisfying combos! Watch as the season beautifully animate and bring the planet back to life, releasing different graphical elements to represent each month.');
