INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(744,326,'ZHTW','掃除戰隊．清潔管理人(日) ','玩家將化身為就讀「高天原高校」，同時還因為委員會選舉當天因缺席而被任命為美化委員長的二年級學生主角「源九郎」，並在某天打掃走廊髒污的時候和「掃除精靈」相遇之後，為了阻止企圖污染學校的「髒亂魔王」的野心守護學園和平，因此必須設法找出跟精靈定下契約的女孩們組成「掃除戰隊」來對抗邪惡魔王！？並跟這些戰隊的女孩夥伴們一起對抗髒亂！');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(745,327,'EN','Sea Monsters: A Prehistoric Adventure','In the oceans of earth millions of years ago, danger was never far away and monsters lurked in every shadow. Experience this astounding world by playing as six different prehistoric marine reptiles, each with special skills – from extreme speed to thick armor and powerful crunching jaws. Start your adventure in an area of inland sea that will only get more dangerous as time passes. Take on foes, hunt for prey and unlock hidden challenges. Your goal is to find a way to truly escape these waters. How to accomplish your escape is something you’ll have to figure out on your journey. Now take control of your first Sea Monster and begin your adventure!');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(746,328,'EN','Sea Monsters: A Prehistoric Adventure','This amazing adaptation of the upcoming National Geograophic film puts you in the role of a giant prehistoric sea creature facing their daily battle to survive. Both fun and educational this is a must have for everyone who loves dinosaurs and prehistoric creatures. The objective of the game is to collect fossil pieces which are hidden throughout the interactive game world. There are 60 pieces in total – 48 creature parts which, when you complete a whole skeleton will unlock a new monster, and 12 wildcard fossils.
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(747,328,'DE','Sea Monsters: A Prehistoric Adventure','In Sea Monsters schlüpft der Spieler in die Haut sechs unterschiedlicher Ozeanmonster die alle über unterschiedliche Fähigkeiten verfügen. Der Spieler begleitet die Ungetüme durch eine gefährliche und stimmungsvolle Unterwasserwelt. Nur wenn die Spezialfähigkeiten der urzeitlichen Monster geschickt eingesetzt werden, kann man dem Schicksal entgehen als Mittagssnack zu enden. Denn: einen größeren gibt es immer! 
