INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(1367,599,'EN','Guitar Hero III Legends Of Rock','Guitar Hero III: Legends of Rock boss battles give fans a chance to compete against legendary guitarists such as Slash and Tom Morello. Players are required to deplete the boss'' Rock Meter before the boss goes into their Death Drain solo, which always means ''lights-out.'' After defeating a boss, players unlock that guitarist as a playable character and continue to the encore for the set list, which is a master recording of one of their respective bands'' most well-known tracks. for instance, When Morello is defeated, the next performance is "Bulls on Parade," during which Morello performs on stage alongside the player. Guitar Hero 3 Features: Slash?s Original Boss Battle Recording Welcome to The Jungle (by Guns N? Roses) One (by Metallica) Paint It Black (by The Rolling Stones) Cherub Rock (by Smashing Pumpkins) Sabotage (by Beastie Boys) The Metal (by Tenacious D) My Name is Jonas (by Weezer) Knights of Cydonia (by Muse) Even Flow (by Pearl Jam) Lay Down (by Priestess) Cult of Personality (by Living Colour) Miss Murder (by AFI) Through Fire and Flames (by Dragonforce) Number of the Beast (by Iron Maiden) 3''s and 7''s (by Queens of the Stone Age) Suck My Kiss (by Red Hot Chili Peppers) Raining Blood (by Slayer) Paranoid (as made famous by Black Sabbath) Cities on Flame (as made famous by Blue Oyster Cult) Mississippi Queen (as made famous by Mountain) La Grange (as made famous by ZZ Top) Rock and Roll All Nite (as made famous by Kiss) School?s Out (as made famous by Alice Cooper) Rock You Like a Hurricane (as made famous by Scorpions) Slow Ride (as made famous by Foghat) Barracuda (as made famous by Heart)');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(1368,599,'FR','Guitar Hero III Legends Of Rock','Montez le volume et préparez-vous à un grand moment de rock: Guitar Hero III: Legends of Rock sur Wii est arrivé! Pour repousser les limites de votre talent, Guitar Hero III vous met une guitare Gibson Les Paul entre les mains et vous invite à entrer en scène pour interpréter certains des plus beaux morceaux de l''histoire du rock.
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(1369,599,'DE','Guitar Hero III: Legends Of Rock','Die Rückkehr auf die Rockbühne. Ran an die Saiten, Verstärker an, es kann gerockt werden. Guitar Hero III: Legends of Rock bringt dich ins Rampenlicht des größten und legendärsten Rockkonzerts aller Zeiten. Der hochkarätige Soundtrack beinhaltet Meisterwerke von Musiklegenden wie etwa den Rolling Stones, Beastie Boys und Pearl Jam. Pack die Luftgitarre in den Schrank, greif dir deinen exklusiven neuen Les Paul Gitarrencontroller und hau mit Guitar Hero III: Legends of Rock nächtelang in die Saiten.');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(1370,599,'IT','Guitar Hero III: Legends Of  Rock','Scatena la rockstar che è in te!
