INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(1652,726,'EN','G.I. JOE: The Rise of Cobra','Suit up, grab your gear and prepare to lock and load as you take control of the elite G.I. JOE® team against the evil forces of COBRA. Based on the upcoming film from Paramount Pictures, the G.I. JOE® video game picks up where the movie leaves off, allowing players to re-create and re-live the greatest moments from the blockbuster film, cartoon and action figure toy line.');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(1653,727,'EN','G.I. JOE: The Rise of Cobra','As COBRA unleashes its deadliest plot yet, the G.I. JOE Team is counting on you and your hand-picked team of heroes to lead the counterattack. Every mission is critical and so is every G.I. JOE character. Picking up where the Paramount Pictures live action film leaves off, G.I. JOE The Rise of Cobra is an accessible third person action-arcade shooter that allows players to recreate and relive the greatest moments from the film, cartoon series and action toy line.
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(1654,727,'FR','G.I. JOE : Le réveil du Cobra','G.I. Joe : Le Réveil du Cobra est un jeu d''action sur Wii. Basé sur l''univers des figurines G.I. Joe, ce titre sorti conjointement avec une oeuvre cinématographique se veut non pas l''adaptation de cette dernière mais le complément. Plutôt axé sur le jeu en coopération, le titre vous propose de retrouver Heavy Duty, le ninja Snake Eyes ou encore une dizaine d''autres personnages dans une aventure riche en action ! ');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(1655,727,'DE','G.I. Joe: Geheimauftrag Cobra','Das einzigartige, vom G.I. JOE-Kinokassenschlager, inspirierte Spiel mit leicht verständlicher Multiplayer-Action. 
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(1656,728,'EN','Truck Racer','Feel the power of these monster racing trucks! They are large, they are fast and they are the most dangerous vehicles to race! Take control of 8 very different types of truck, and find out which one is the best! Full of action and danger, this is high-octane power racing!
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(1657,728,'DE','Truck Racer','Sie sind groß, sie sind schnell und sie sind die gefährlichsten Rennwagen, die die Straße je gesehen hat. Übernehmen Sie die Kontrolle über 8 komplett verschiedene Arten von Trucks und finden Sie heraus, welcher der Beste ist. Truck Racer ist voll gepackt mit knallharter Action und vielen Gefahren. 
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(1658,729,'EN','Illust Logic + Colorful Logic','');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(1659,729,'JA','パズルシリーズ Vol.2 イラストロジック+からふるロジック','');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(1660,730,'EN','Impossible Mission','The gamer takes the role of a secret agent attempting to stop evil genius Professor Elvin Atombender who has been tampering with National Security Computers. Players must penetrate Atombender''s base, attempting to recover parts of the system password whilst avoiding deadly robots in a race against time. Whilst the game has been re-written from the ground up and features new graphics, 3D objects, new Sound Effects and Music, the gameplay remains loyal with the game layout changing for every new game. There are now three main characters to choose from plus a brand new tutorial mode. The player can now chose from three game modes, new, original and for the purist; a hybrid mode with the original gameplay using the updated graphics.');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(1661,731,'EN','Impossible Mission','');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(1662,731,'FR','Impossible Mission','Impossible Mission sur Wii est le remake du vieux jeu de plates-formes dans lequel vous incarnez un agent secret chargé de neutraliser le professeur Atombender avant qu''il ne parvienne à pirater le système informatique du gouvernement. Votre mission, si vous l''acceptez, est de récupérer des indices permettant d''atteindre le système central et de le détruire.');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(1663,731,'DE','Impossible Mission','Alleine als Agent im Hauptquartier des Feindes. Aber es ist eine Falle. In einem Labyrinth aus Gängen und Fahrstühlen. Nur 20:00 Minuten um alle versteckten Puzzleteile in den von Hinterhalten und Wachrobotern beschützten Räumen der unterirdischen Basis zu finden. Nur 20:00 Minuten, um alle Rätsel zu lösen. Nur 20:00 Minuten, um zu entkommen und zu überleben. 
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(1664,732,'EN','Dead Rising: Chop Till You Drop','Dead Rising: Chop Till You Drop follows the harrowing tale of Frank West, an overly zealous freelance journalist on a hunt for the scoop of a lifetime. In pursuit of a juicy lead, he makes his way to the small suburban town of Willamette only to find that it has become overrun by zombies. Frank escapes to the local shopping mall, thinking it will be a bastion of safety but it turns out to be anything but. It will be a true struggle to survive the endless stream of enemies, but players will have full reign of a realistic shopping centre and its varied stores offering an endless supply of real and makeshift weapons to fight off the flesh-hungry mob. If Frank is running low on health he can pay a visit to one of the many restaurants or cafes for a meal in order to restore his energy and continue the fight. The game is split into a series of individual cases, all of which Frank must complete in order to gain vital information that will allow him to piece together the truth behind the horrendous epidemic. In addition to the cases, players will be faced with the dilemma of deciding the rescue priority of the residents of Wilamette who also sought sanctuary in the mall. Depending on the player''s skill, some may not be so fortunate as each rescue needs to be undertaken in a set time period, therefore players may need to delay completion of a case in order to save a fellow human. Dead Rising: Chop Till You Drop''s infectious humor delivers some welcome relief from the incessant tide of zombies with players able to dress Frank up in a variety of comedic costumes and take on the undead hordes with a selection of improvised and sometimes highly ineffective weapons such as a toy sword or a football.');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(1665,733,'EN','Dead Rising Zombie No Ikenie','');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(1666,733,'JA','デッドライジング ゾンビのいけにえ','');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(1667,734,'EN','Dead Rising: Chop Till You Drop','Based on the critically acclaimed ''Dead Rising'' for the Xbox 360, Dead Rising: Chop Till You Drop follows the harrowing tale of Frank West, an overly zealous freelance journalist on a hunt for the scoop of a lifetime. In pursuit of a juicy lead, he makes his way to the small suburban town of Willamette only to find that it has become overrun by zombies. Frank escapes to the local shopping mall where he thinks he will find safety only to discover its crawling with the un-dead!
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(1668,734,'FR','Dead Rising: Chop Till You Drop','Les morts-vivants reviennent en force avec Dead Rising: Chop Till You Drop. Retrouvez la tension horrifique, l''adrénaline et l''humour noir typiques d''un film de zombies sur votre Wii. Grâce au même moteur de jeu que Resident Evil 4 sur Wii, l''amateur chasseur de zombies que vous êtes va avoir sa dose d''action dans les couloirs du grand centre commercial infesté de créatures dévoreuses de cervelle qui traînent des pieds. Vous disposez de tout un arsenal mortel pour arrêter net ces zombies morts-vivants!
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(1669,734,'DE','Dead Rising: Chop Till You Drop','Das Kultspiel von der Xbox 360 wird nun von den gleichen Entwicklern auch für die Nintendo Wii umgesetzt. Die Story wird dabei etwas umstrukturiert damit das Spiel leichter zugänglich wird.
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(1670,734,'ES','Dead Rising: Terror en el Hipermercado','Juego de acción (tipo survival horror) protagonizado por Frank, un periodista que se encuentra encerrado en un gigantesco centro comercial plagado por miles de zombies. Una de las principales características de Dead Rising, es la posibilidad de enfrentarse a los enemigos pudiendo lanzar y usar cualquier tipo de objeto que encontremos.
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(1671,735,'EN','Horrible Histories: Ruthless Romans','The Horrible Histories™ brand is an internationally bestselling series of history books for children, with more than 20 million copies sold worldwide since 1993. Author Terry Deary and illustrator Martin Brown have brought the past to life for millions of children in an uniquely entertaining way. The computer game version of their Ruthless Romans book will provide whole families with a fun way to learn about Roman history. The main plot of Horrible Histories™ Ruthless Romans follows the struggle of young Rassimus to achieve glory as a gladiator and obtain his freedom. Rassimus, a slave and an ambitious gladiator-in-training, has been raised as a foundling by the great gladiator trainer Lucius Gladius, and spent nearly 12 years in his service. Lucius has now given him a chance to begin his training, and Rassimus hopes that he will be successful and one day become a citizen of Rome.
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(1672,735,'FR','Horribles Histoires: les Redoutables Romains','Horribles Histoires : Les Redoutables Romains sur Wii est un jeu d''aventure ponctué de mini-jeux qui prend place dans la Rome Antique. Ce titre allie humour et divertissement dans un contexte historique fidèlement reproduit à travers 7 scénarios. Incarnez un jeune gladiateur qui rêve de faire carrière au Colisée !');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(1673,735,'DE','Schauderhafte Geschichten: Skrupellose Römer','');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(1674,735,'ES','Esa Horrible Historia: Depravados Romanos','');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(1675,736,'EN','One Piece: Unlimited Adventure','Avast ye land lubbers! Hoist anchor and set sail for a brand new One Piece adventure exclusively for the Nintendo Wii. Join Luffy and the rest of the Straw Hat Pirates as they search for the ultimate treasure in a brand new quest.
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(1676,737,'EN','One Piece Unlimited Adventure','');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(1677,737,'JA','ワンピース アンリミテッドアドベンチャー','不思議な島を舞台にルフィたち麥わら海賊団が大冒険を繰り広げる、ワンピース初のアクションアドベンチャーゲーム！プレイヤーは麥わら海賊団８人の中から場面に合わせキャラクターを選択し、謎に満ちた不思議な島を冒険します。もちろん行く手には、ルフィたちを苦しめた原作の強敵たちも続々登場。大勢の敵との多人數戦から強力なボスとの１vs.１の対決まで、バトルも盛りだくさん！そしてバトル以外にも冒険を盛り上げる様々なアクションが満載。アイテムにある「釣り竿」「ツルハシ」「蟲取り網」を使用する際は、Ｗｉｉリモコンを振ったり傾けたりとＷｉｉならではのコントローラ操作をします。敵と戦うだけでなく、のんびりとワンピースの世界を味わうことができます。');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(1678,737,'ZHTW','海賊王．無盡的冒險(日) ','');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(1679,738,'EN','One Piece Unlimited Cruise 1 - The Treasure Beneath the Waves ','');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(1680,738,'FR','One Piece Unlimited Cruise 1: Le Trésor sous les Flots','One Piece Unlimited Cruise 1: Le Trésor sous les Flots est un jeu d''action/aventure qui s''inspire du manga de Eiichiro Oda. L''équipage de Luffy part explorer cinq îles hostiles où il devra affronter la plupart des boss les plus connus de la série. Un mode Versus permet d''incarner jusqu''à 30 personnages différents.');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(1681,738,'DE','One Piece Unlimited Cruise 1 - Der Schatz unter den Wellen ','Endlich wird die One Piece-Serie neu aufgelegt. In Unlimited Cruise 1 sticht der bekannte Titelheld mit Strohhut und eiserner Crew wieder in unbekannte Gewässer vor. Exklusiv für Wii! In „One Piece Unlimited Cruise: Der Schatz unter den Wellen“ werden alle bekannten Helden des Mangas erneut vereint, um an der Seite des Titelhelden Ruffy gegen das Böse zu kämpfen.
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(1682,739,'EN','Iron Man','Tony Stark had it all: a genius mind, fame, and even a multinational corporation. But his life would soon change forever. During a routine weapons test in the Middle East, power-hungry militants led a violent ambush against Tony and claimed him as their prisoner. Armed with Stark Industries weaponry, Tony’s new foes demanded he construct a new ultimate weapon for them. Instead, with the help of fellow captive Yinsen, Tony built his own ultimate weapon – a powerful suit of armor that served as the key to his heroic escape.
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(1683,740,'EN','Iron Man','');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(1684,740,'FR','Iron Man','En tant qu''adaptation officielle du film, Iron Man sur Wii reprend les moments forts vus sur grand écran. Sous les traits métalliques du super héros, le joueur peut compter sur la grande rapidité et la puissance de feu de son armure pour traverser les niveaux de ce jeu d''action.');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(1685,740,'DE','Iron Man: The Video Game','Iron Man™, der unbesiegbare Superheld von Marvel, erobert die Videospiel-Plattformen. Kämpfe im High-Tech-Anzug und mit zahlreichen Waffen auf dynamisch herausfordernden Schlachtfeldern, gegen Armeen gnadenloser Gegner. In diesem 3rd Person Action-Game erwarten dich zudem spannende Sequenzen aus dem Film. Tauche mitten in die explosive militärische Kampf-Action ein und entdecke jede Menge zusätzliche, exklusiv für das Spiel erschaffene Inhalte. 
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(1686,741,'EN','Intervilles, le jeu officiel','');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(1687,741,'FR','Intervilles, le jeu officiel','Tout Intervilles dans votre salon ! Mais attention, Rosa la vachette n’est pas loin et son passe-temps favori est de faire chuter les candidats !
