INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(1869,835,'EN','Rock Band','Rock Band for Wii features over 60 songs ranging across all genres of rock, including five extra bonus tracks exclusive to the disc for Wii gamers!
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(1870,836,'EN','Rock Band','');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(1871,836,'FR','Rock Band','Rock Band sur Wii a pour but de vous placer au coeur d''un groupe de rock. En utilisant les accessoires conçus pour le jeu, vous pourrez au choix vous asseoir derrière la batterie, jouer de la guitare ou de la basse ou même chanter dans le micro. Evidemment, Rock Band encourage vivement de se retrouver entre amis pour former un groupe entier et jouer en même temps sur des morceaux connus.');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(1872,837,'EN','Army Men: Soldiers of Misfortune','Assume the role of Timmy, mini action adventure hero, and fight the forces of evil in "Army Men: Soldiers of Misfortune." Timmy''s Tan Army Men action figures have run amok, capturing his Green Army Men, and attempting to take control of his little slice of suburbia! It''s up to you to defeat the enemy, save your toys and family, and restore order to your home! The house is your playground as you control a 3 inch tall Timmy and a slew of toy weaponry to keep his tan Army Men from achieving "Global Home Domination." You''ll never look at your toys the same again...');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(1873,838,'EN','Army Men: Soldiers Of Misfortune','');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(1874,839,'EN','Army Men Soldiers of misfortune','Assume the role of Timmy, mini action adventure hero, and fight the forces of evil in "Army Men :Soldiers of Misfortune." Timmy''s Tan Army Men action figures have run amok, capturing his Green Army Men, and attempting to take control of his little slice of suburbia! It''s up to you to defeat the enemy, save your toys and family, and restore order to your home! The house is your playground as you control a 3 inch tall Timmy and a slew of toy weaponry to keep his tan Army Men from achieving "Global Home Domination." You''ll never look at your toys the same again... 
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(1875,839,'DE','Army Men: Soldiers of Misfortune','Hilf Timmy, der dir all seine Spielzeuge zur Verfügung stellt, dabei, die Army Men: Soldiers of Misfortune aufzuspüren! Requiriere Panzer, Jeeps & Flugzeuge, eliminiere die gegnerischen Truppen mit Schaumstoff-Projektilen, Tennisbällen, Flaschenverschlüssen & Wasser, befreue die verbündete Grüne Brigade und bringe wieder Frieden in Timmys Heim - und all dies unter dem Befehl von General Teddy!');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(1876,840,'EN','Lost in Blue: Shipwrecked','You find yourself stranded on a mysterious island filled with lush forests, a sunken ship, ancient ruins, and an active volcano. With the help of a trusty pet and a new friend, you''ll explore the mysteries of the island to find a way out or make a new life for yourselves there forever. ');
