INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(2165,972,'EN','Marvel : Ultimate Alliance 2','The largest army of Super Heroes is back… and being torn apart! The Superhuman Registration Act becomes law and Super Heroes must register as weapons of mass destruction, becoming licensed government agents. As Civil War is stirred, Iron Man leads the Pro-Registration side while Captain America spearheads the stand on Anti-Registration. The fate of the Marvel Universe is in your hands. Lines are drawn. Sides are chosen. And the ultimate question remains: Whose side are you on?
