INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(2210,994,'EN','Dawn of Discovery','Dawn of Discovery takes place in the year 1404, when King George’s land is suffering from severe droughts and brutal famine. Aware of his people’s distress, the king calls on his two sons, William and Edward, to acquire new territories in order to produce enough goods to satisfy the needs of his empire’s inhabitants. Whereas Edward suggests aggressive means to collect the precious resources, his brother William offers a peaceful solution, proposing to explore new and unsettled lands in the south of the kingdom.
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(2211,995,'EN','Anno: Create a New World','Anno: Create a New World, takes place in year 1404, where King George''s land suffers from drought and famine. Aware of the distress of his citizens, he decides to remedy the situation by sending his two sons, William and Edward, to explore new fertile territories that could produce enough goods to satisfy his people. Despite being brothers, both sons have very different personalities; where Edward suggests fighting to collect the resources they need, his brother William offers a more peaceful approach, suggesting they explore new and unsettled lands to the south.
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(2212,995,'FR','Anno: Créez votre Monde','Anno : Créez Votre Monde sur Wii est un jeu de gestion dans lequel vous incarnez un prince parti coloniser des terres exotiques. Après avoir choisi une île, il lui faudra fonder une colonie et veiller au bonheur de ses sujets. Il pourra alors lever des impôts et assurer le développement de sa ville et de ses infrastructures. Le jeu propose un mode Campagne, un mode Libre et un mode deux joueurs en coopération.');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(2213,995,'DE','ANNO - Erschaffe eine neue Welt','ANNO - Eine einzigartige und preisgekrönte Kombination aus Aufbau, Wirtschaft, Entdeckung, Diplomatie und Kampf. Auf geht es in den offiziellen vierten Teil der beliebten Aufbaustrategieserie. In ANNO: Erschaffe eine neue Welt geht es in den Orient und dort warten viele neue Features, Völker, Waren und vieles mehr auf dich. Nur durch geschickten Handel, gerissene Diplomatie und zukunftsorientierte Bauplanung kann die eigene Insel florieren und gedeihen. 
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(2214,995,'ES','ANNO: La Creación de Un Nuevo Mundo','CARACTERÍSTICAS CLAVE
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(2215,995,'IT','Anno: Crea un Nuovo Mondo','Conscio della situazione drammatica del suo popolo, il sovrano decide di inviare i suoi due figli, William ed Edward, a cercare nuovi territori per produrre risorse a sufficienza a soddisfare gli abitanti. Mentre Edward suggerisce di combattere per ottenere le preziose risorse, suo fratello William offre una soluzione più pacifica, proponendo di esplorare nuove e sconosciute lande nella parte meridionale del regno. Con l’autorizzazione di suo padre, William si dirige quindi verso sud scoprendo così la misteriosa cultura orientale.
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(2216,996,'EN','The Naked Brothers Band: The Video Game','Become a part of the Naked Brothers Band Tour! Use your Wii remote and nunchuk or microphone to sing along and play up to 5 instruments as each member of the band. Includes 25 of your favorite Naked Brothers Band songs. Play to unlock new songs, concert venues, outfits, instruments and more! ');
