INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(2269,1026,'EN','NHL 2K9','2K Sports is bringing the fun back to hockey video games with an intuitive control scheme and hard-hitting action. As the first & only officially licensed NHL and NHLPA video game for Wii, NHL 2K9 will offer fans the opportunity to play like the pros using the Wii Remote as a hockey stick and experience the sport in a new, entertaining and wholly unique manner. ');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(2270,1027,'EN','NHL 2K9','');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(2271,1027,'FR','NHL 2K9','NHL 2K9 est un jeu de hockey sur glace sur Wii. Il propose des mouvements tels que les tirs bloqués, gère les collisions avec le palet et présente plus de 1400 nouvelles animations. Des commentaires de Randy Hahn et Drew Remenda donnent vie aux matches. La bande-son très punk-rock fait notamment appel à Pennywise, Bad Religion, The Offspring, NOFX et aux Ramones.');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(2272,1027,'DE','NHL 2K9','Zahlreiche Gameplay-Features: NHL 2K9 bietet kurzweiliges Eishockey-Gameplay mit rasanter Multiplayer-Action, Pond-Hockey, einem Franchise-Modus, Spezialmoves und und und!
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(2273,1028,'EN','Ninjabread Man','This once sweet and tasty land has been taken over by hordes of snapping Cup Cakes, Angry Bees and Jelly Monsters.
