INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(2430,1093,'EN','Offroad Extreme Special Edition','This is the super-charged turbo driven world of Offroad Extreme where intense, free-roaming, off-road racing takes on a whole new meaning!
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(2431,1094,'EN','Offroad Extreme!','Enter the super-charged turbo driven world of Off Road Extreme. This is where off road racing takes on a whole new meaning! From Karts to Baja Buggies, Offroad Extreme delivers a unique and exciting gamplay experience. You will race a variety of off road vehicles through visually stunning environments, around rugged terrain, along valleys and through ancient cave structures. Choose from a vast selection of detailed off road machines with an impressive 32 unique track variations including quarries, canyons and mines. Featuring realistic weather conditions during day and night. Earn prize money to unlock hidden extras, including upgrades, extra challenges, extra courses and much more. Utilising the Wii controls to allow you to use the wireless Wii Remote as a steering wheel. Be careful though, every time your vehicle takes some on damage you will have to pay for your repairs.');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(2432,1094,'FR','Offroad Extreme!','Offroad Extreme! sur Wii est un jeu de courses proposant de courir à bord de buggys. S''étalant sur 3 modes de jeu, il vous faut terminer les circuits un à un si vous voulez débloquer le suivant. Le titre propose un mode deux joueurs via un écran séparé en deux.');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(2433,1095,'EN','Tak and the Guardians of Gross','As the keeper of the power of Juju, it''s Tak''s responsibility to care for the sacred Juju shrines. Unfortunately, Tak accidentally frees the four "Grosstrosities" — Stink Giant, Slime Giant, Landfill Giant, and Molten Cheese Giant who were trapped in the shrine. These giants were trapped because they were so disgusting that they were just too gross to walk the earth. Tak must seek the help of the "Big G''s" four master Jujus in order to defeat the giants before they cover the world in their stinky foulness. ');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(2434,1096,'EN','Tak And The Guardians Of Gross','As the keeper of the power of Juju, it''s Tak''s responsibility to care for the sacred Juju shrines. Unfortunately, Tak accidentally frees the four "Grosstrosities" — Stink Giant, Slime Giant, Landfill Giant, and Molten Cheese Giant who were trapped in the shrine. These giants were trapped because they were so disgusting that they were just too gross to walk the earth. Tak must seek the help of the "Big G''s" four master Jujus in order to defeat the giants before they cover the world in their stinky foulness.');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(2435,1096,'FR','Tak And The Guardians Of Gross','Tak and the Guardians of Gross sur Wii vous plonge dans les aventures du héros éponyme à la recherche d''un sanctuaire d''où provient une mystérieuse magie. A peine prend-il le cristal qui en est à l''origine que celui-ci éclate en 100 fragments, libérant par là même 4 géants au demeurant peu amènes et sympathiques. Lourde tâche en perspective que de réparer le caillou magique... ');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(2436,1096,'DE','Tak - Das Geheimnis des glühenden Kristalls',' Tak ist zurück! Der lebenslustige junge Schamane tobt wieder durch den Dschungel und erlebt neue Abenteuer. Tak hat momentan aber ein klitzekleines Problem: er hat versehentlich einen glühenden Kristall in einem heiligen Schrein zerstört! 
