INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(2474,1112,'EN','Okami','The multiple award-winning Okami returns for a glorious encore on the Wii! Amaterasu, the wolf-embodied sun god must breathe color and life into a world made dismal by the tyrannical and destructive monster Orochi. Amaterasu travels through various regions of the world to regain "Celestial Brush" powers, all the while revitalizing all life. Featuring a re-imagined control scheme built around the intuitive Wii Remote, Okami for the Wii offers players an unparalleled level of control and an opportunity to rediscover a critically-acclaimed and beautifully crafted adventure.');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(2475,1113,'EN','Okami','The multiple award-winning Okami returns for a glorious encore on the Wii! Amaterasu, the wolf-embodied sun god must breathe color and life into a world made dismal by the tyrannical and destructive monster Orochi. Amaterasu travels through various regions of the world to regain "Celestial Brush" powers, all the while revitalizing all life. Featuring a re-imagined control scheme built around the intuitive Wii Remote, Okami for the Wii offers players an unparalleled level of control and an opportunity to rediscover a critically-acclaimed and beautifully crafted adventure.');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(2476,1113,'FR','Okami','Alors que certains jeux donnent l''impression d''avoir été dessinés aux crayons de couleurs par un enfant de 4 ans, Ōkami est une œuvre d''art à laquelle vous apportez votre touche avec un pinceau peu ordinaire, la télécommande Wii.
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(2477,1113,'DE','Okami','Es stimmt ja – manche Spiele geben einem das Gefühl, dass sie durch Malen nach Zahlen erstellt wurden. „Okami“ dagegen malt in ganz eigenem Stil und verwendet die Wii-Fernbedienung als Pinsel.
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(2478,1113,'ES','Okami','Clover Studio creadores la saga Viewtiful Joe vuelve a apostar por un original e innovador título en el que controlaremos a una diosa que adopta forma de loba, para salvar a la humanidad y devolverle su creencia en los dioses y la naturaleza.
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(2479,1113,'NL','Okami','Hoewel sommige spellen lijken te zijn vormgegeven aan de hand van schilderen-op-nummer, schildert Ōkami de vakjes in een compleet eigen stijl, en gebruikt het de Wii-afstandsbediening als kwast.
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(2480,1114,'EN','Order Up!','Order Up is a delicious blend of precision cuisine crafting and culinary empire building, all rolled into a light and flaky crust of memorable characters and humorous situations. With the Wii Remote in hand, the player will be guided from burger to chateaubriand; taught every aspect of food preparation and presentation. For anyone who has dreamed of becoming a world-class chef or restaurant mogul or both!, Order Up will deliver. The core game play of Order Up is cooking, from preparation to presentation. Preparation consists of "cutting and cooking" while Presentation refers to garnishes and "flourishes" - e.g. sauce drizzled over a dish to please the eye or the use of flame (flambé) for dramatic effect. Beyond the core, game play includes rising through the ranks of the culinary world from fast-food to world-class restaurants as chef and owner while ever-expanding your cookbook of recipes and ever-improving the quality of your equipment. Along the way you will face demanding patrons, discriminating food critics…and at the pinnacle of your fame in the world of fine cuisine you will be invited to complete in the, "Fortified Chef World Challenge" - an Iron Chef-style cooking competition.');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(2481,1115,'EN','Order Up!','Order Up is a delicious blend of precision cuisine crafting and culinary empire building, all rolled into a light and flaky crust of memorable characters and humorous situations. With the Wii Remote in hand, the player will be guided from burger to chateaubriand; taught every aspect of food preparation and presentation. For anyone who has dreamed of becoming a world-class chef or restaurant mogul or both!, Order Up will deliver. The core game play of Order Up is cooking, from preparation to presentation. Preparation consists of "cutting and cooking" while Presentation refers to garnishes and "flourishes" - e.g. sauce drizzled over a dish to please the eye or the use of flame (flambé) for dramatic effect. Beyond the core, game play includes rising through the ranks of the culinary world from fast-food to world-class restaurants as chef and owner while ever-expanding your cookbook of recipes and ever-improving the quality of your equipment. Along the way you will face demanding patrons, discriminating food critics…and at the pinnacle of your fame in the world of fine cuisine you will be invited to complete in the, "Fortified Chef World Challenge" - an Iron Chef-style cooking competition. ');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(2482,1115,'FR','Order Up!','Order up! place le joueur dans la cuisine d''un restaurant sur Wii. Il doit s''occuper de la vaisselle et de la cuisson, diriger les cuisiniers assistants, faire face aux demandes du patron et aux critiques culinaires. Au sommet de la gloire, il s''agit de gérer de multiples restaurants et de créer de nouveaux plats.');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(2483,1116,'EN','Order Up!','Order Up! is a delicious blend of frantic kitchen cooking and restaurant empire building.  Chop, roll, slice, and dice your way to culinary stardom.  Along the way you will face picky patrons, snobby food critics, one grouchy health inspector, and more.
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(2484,1116,'DE','Order Up!','Zum aller ersten Mal können Sie auf der Wii Ihr eigenes Restaurant führen! Als armer Koch in einem Fastfood-Laden beschließen Sie ein eigenes Restaurant zu eröffnen. Dies ist der Start und Ihre Chance für eine spektakuläre Karriere in der Welt der Starköche. Sind Sie bereit sich gegen die Konkurrenz durchzusetzen und der beste Koch der Welt zu werden? 
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(2485,1117,'EN','Cloudy with a chance of Meat Ball','Play as Flint, the wacky inventor who creates a machine that causes food to rain from the sky! When the machine spirals out of control, it’s up to you to save the town with a variety of outrageously fun and wacky gadgets. Hurl hamburgers, sling spaghetti, and join the most hilarious food fight ever!
