INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(2627,1182,'EN','Mad Dog McCree Gunslinger Pack','The live action, six-shooting, Wild West adventures of Mad Dog McCree are blazing their way to your Wii. Take on the role of the Bounty Hunter in this collection of all three classic arcade shooters: Mad Dog McCree, Mad Dog 2: The Lost Gold, and The Last 
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(2628,1183,'EN','Mad Dog McCree : Gunslinger Pack','');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(2629,1184,'EN','Mad Dog McCree Gunslinger Pack','Three-In-One Collection of Classic Mad Dog McCree Arcade Games Debuts as the First Live-Action Shooter on Wii!
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(2630,1185,'EN','Cursed Mountain','Frank Simmons will never stop trying to find his brother. When his brother went missing during a trek to the Himalayas to find an ancient Buddhist artifact, Frank set out for the mountains to track him down. Using controls designed specifically for the Wii, explore a realistic and daunting mountain environment. As you ascend the mountain, you''ll see the summit in the distance - a looming reminder of your final destination. With rituals, mantras, and gestures, you will use your spirit to defeat enemies. Reach the top to determine the fate of Frank''s brother.');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(2631,1186,'EN','Cursed Mountain','This survival horror game follows an experienced climber who sets out to scale a huge mountain in the Himalayas in order to find his recently-lost brother. As he ascends the mountain, he encounters an ancient curse: the souls of the people who died in that region are stuck in limbo, caught in the Shadow World. Players must content with villagers, pilgrims, mountaineers, Buddhist monks, and evil ghosts and demons as they unravel the mystery of the location. And for what? The climber isn''t at all convinced that his missing brother is still alive...');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(2632,1186,'FR','Cursed Mountain','Dans Cursed Mountain, le joueur incarne Eric Simmons, un alpiniste expérimenté partant à l''assaut du Chomolonzo, une montagne sacrée de l''Himalaya, pour tenter de lever le voile sur la disparition soudaine de son frère.
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(2633,1186,'DE','Cursed Mountain','Das einzigartige Survival-Horrorspiel "Cursed Mountain" spielt in der faszinierenden und stimmungsvollen Welt des mystischen Tibet, vor der Kulisse der verlassenen Eisgipfel des Himalaja. Der Spieler macht sich auf die Suche nach seinem Bruder, der vor kurzer Zeit bei einer Expedition verschwand. Unter extremsten Bedingungen kämpft der Spieler dabei nicht nur gegen die lebensfeindliche Umwelt, sondern auch gegen übernatürliche Gegner.
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(2634,1186,'ES','Cursed Mountain','En Cursed Mountain, los jugadores toman el papel de Eric Simmons, un experto montañero que se encuentra escalando el Chomolonzo, una montaña sagrada de la cordillera del Himalaya, intentando desentrañar el misterio que rodea a la repentina desaparición de su hermano.
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(2635,1186,'IT','Cursed Mountain','Preparati ad entrare in uno spaventoso mondo di orribili maledizioni, segreti diabolici e disperati sforzi per sopravvivere nelle condizioni più dure del pianeta. Preparati ad entrare in Cursed Mountain per Wii.
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(2636,1187,'EN','Moto GP 08','Experience the intensity, thrills and excitement of motorcycle racing with MotoGP. Join a team and compete against world-class opponents in three separate classes, on exotic courses all over the world. Show off your skills and take risks to earn points and upgrade your bike. And with new, easy-to-learn controls, MotoGP is the most accessible motorcycle racing game to date. ');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(2637,1188,'EN','MotoGP 08','MotoGP 08 puts the player at the centre of the MotoGP experience by letting them join a team and compete alongside their sporting heroes in all three race classes 125cc, 250cc and MotoGP. Good results in qualifying and racing earn points that can then be exchanged for bike upgrades to improve attributes such as straight line speed, braking and cornering.');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(2638,1188,'FR','MotoGP 08','MotoGP 08 est un jeu de courses sur Wii avec, au menu, les véhicules, les pilotes et les circuits officiels de la saison 2008. Trois catégories de motos sont disponibles (125cc, 250 cc et MotoGP) ainsi que trois niveaux de réalisme (arcade, intermédiaire et simulation). L''intelligence artificielle des concurrents s''adapte au niveau du joueur.');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(2639,1188,'DE','Moto GP','Motoren heulen auf. Reifen quietschen und der Sound von "MotoGP" begleitet dich durch das packendste Rennereignis der Welt. Dieses ultimative Rennerlebnis verzeiht keine Fehler und geht keine Kompromisse ein. Es kommt einzig und allein auf dein fahrerisches Können an. So fühlt es sich an.');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(2640,1188,'IT','MotoGP 08','MotoGP 08, il videogioco ufficiale della MotoGP, presenta tutti I piloti, I tracciati e le moto ufficiale, per una incredibile esperienza di gioco che farà vivere le gare con un realismo mai visto prima.
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(2641,1189,'EN','NBA Live 09 All-Play','NBA LIVE 09 is back. It rewrites the book on authenticity and connectivity - but is still accessible enough for new users. Dynamic DNA emulates - with absolute precision - an NBA player in every sense of the word. NBA LIVE 365 takes the statistical data of Dynamic DNA and brings it to life. Just like the real NBA game, players get injured, free agents sign late, great players go cold and no-names break through.');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(2642,1190,'EN','NBA Live 09 All-Play','');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(2643,1190,'FR','NBA Live 09 All-Play','NBA Live 09 All-Play est un jeu de basket sur Wii doté d''une licence enrichie: 24 équipes nationales peuvent s''affronter dans un tournoi international, avec notamment la France, l''Espagne et les Etats-Unis. Le mode multijoueur autorise la participation de huit personnes en ligne contre quatre en local.');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(2644,1190,'DE','NBA Live 09 All-Play','NBA LIVE 09 ist da! Der jüngste Teil der Kult-Basketballreihe bietet unvergleichlichen Realismus auf tagesaktueller Basis und ist trotz seiner spielerischen Tiefe auch für Einsteiger sofort zugänglich. 
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(2645,1191,'EN','NBA Live 09 All-Play','');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(2646,1191,'ES','NBA Live 09 All-Play','');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(2647,1192,'EN','Kawasaki Quad Bikes','Tear around offroad tracks in Kawasaki Quad Bikes for Nintendo Wii. This racer is the ultimate quad biking experience, putting you in the driver''s seat of these awesome All Terrain Vehicles. Feel the thrill of overtaking your opponents at high speeds and catch crazy air to make the whole arena roar. ');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(2648,1193,'EN','Kawasaki Quad Bikes','Kawasaki Quad Bikes is the ultimate quad biking experience putting you in the driving seat of these awesome All Terrain Vehicles. Feel the thrill of overtaking your opponents at high speed and catch crazy air to make the whole arena roar! A full range of officially licensed Kawasaki Quad Bikes, with unlockable extras, hidden quads, upgrades, courses and much more. Kawasaki Quad Bikes features the most exhilarating off road tracks known to man! This is a chance to experience the heart stopping power and agility of these awesome Kawasaki machines. Outstanding single player game modes include numerous championship and single race challenges, with over 70 track variations. Multiplayer mode allows you to compete against friends, with lots of challenging environments to explore, from gravel covered slopes to mud soaked arenas.');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(2649,1194,'EN','Kawasaki Quad Bikes','This is the ultimate quad biking experience putting you in the driving seat of one of these awesome All Terrain Vehicles. The game features the most exhilarating off road tracks known to man. Plus you will experience the heart stopping power and agility of these awesome machines.');
