INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(2720,1224,'EN','Fantasy Aquarium World','Your Wii becomes a virtual fish tank in Fantasy Aquarium World from Destineer! Pick your fish, decorate your tank and balance species for the ideal aquatic ecosystem. Under the watchful eye of the Captain, feed and care for over 30 species of fish, from the common seahorse to the legendary Loch Ness Monster!');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(2721,1225,'EN','Rig Racer 2','Get behind the wheel of these mammoth trucks and roll out onto some of the craziest racetracks around.Ever wanted to drive a Big Rig? How about speed around a racetrack in one? Well now you can experience the thrill in Rig Racer 2!
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(2722,1226,'EN','Rig Racer 2','Ever fancied driving a rig? How about speeding around a track in one? Well now you can experience the thrill in Rig Racer 2! Get prepared for the toughest race experience on the Wii. Keep on truckin''… ');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(2723,1227,'EN','Build-A-Bear Workshop: A Friend Fur All Seasons','Your furry friend is invited to a great party on Palace Island by Bearemy and Pawlette. In order to cross the sea and reach the party, Bearemy and Pawlette offer you the FriendShip. Explore new islands on the way and take time to meet and interact with the furry friends that live there. They love playing games too, so on each island you get to play mini games, help them out, and find the puzzle pieces needed to recreate the map that will lead you to the next island. Finally you reach Palace Island where a big party awaits you!');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(2724,1228,'EN','Build-A-Bear Workshop','Your furry friend is invited to a great party on Palace Island by Bearemy and Pawlette. In order to cross the sea and reach the party, Bearemy and Pawlette offer you the FriendShip. Explore new islands on the way and take time to meet and interact with the furry friends that live there. They love playing games too, so on each island you get to play mini games, help them out, and find the puzzle pieces needed to recreate the map that will lead you to the next island. Finally you reach Palace Island where a big party awaits you! ');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(2725,1228,'FR','Build-A-Bear Workshop','Build-a-Bear Workshop sur Wii est un titre reprenant une très célèbre franchise américaine permettant de se fabriquer le nounours idéal. Choisissez parmi un nombre très varié d''accessoires, de couleurs, de forme, de taille, le tout avec la Wiimote et le Nunchuk. Une fois cela accompli, jouez avec votre peluche et emmenez-la partout avec vous.');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(2726,1229,'EN','Ready 2 Rumble Revolution','The famed boxing franchise Ready 2 Rumble returns in 2009 when Atari launches Ready 2 Rumble: Revolution. Whilst maintaining all the humorous caricatures and fun boxing action that made the original Ready 2 Rumble Boxing Round1 and Round2 (Midway) such knock-out best-sellers, the new digitally sophisticated and visually stunning motion-controlled Ready 2 Rumble: Revolution for Wii brings a new level of style and attitude to the boxing ring and continues the franchise with a host of hard-hitting enhancements.');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(2727,1230,'EN','Ready 2 Rumble Revolution','The famed boxing franchise Ready 2 Rumble returns in 2009 when Atari launches Ready 2 Rumble: Revolution. Whilst maintaining all the humorous caricatures and fun boxing action that made the original Ready 2 Rumble Boxing Round1 and Round2 (Midway) such knock-out best-sellers, the new digitally sophisticated and visually stunning motion-controlled Ready 2 Rumble: Revolution for Wii brings a new level of style and attitude to the boxing ring and continues the franchise with a host of hard-hitting enhancements.');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(2728,1230,'FR','Ready 2 Rumble Revolution','Après des années de silence, la série Ready 2 Rumble remonte sur le ring pour déverser une série d''uppercuts et de crochets bien sentis. Le look cartoon et les personnalités caricaturées donnent un esprit très second degré à ce jeu de combat sur Wii. Il est possible de créer son propre sportif et de le suivre au fil des matches.');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(2729,1231,'EN','Real Madrid The Game','');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(2730,1231,'FR','Real de Madrid','Real de Madrid sur Wii est un jeu de football centré autour de la célèbre équipe madrilène. Il propose aux joueurs de participer à la vie du club, tant dans les aspects humains que sportifs. Il est également possible de simuler sa carrière au sein du club.');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(2731,1232,'EN','WWE SmackDown! vs. RAW 2009','The #1 fighting game franchise in the world upholds its commitment to providing gamers with the definitive simulation of live WWE programming. Featuring added depth and realism, along with a first-ever co-op storyline, WWE SmackDown vs. Raw 2009 enables players to come together and experience the virtual world of the WWE. On your own, you''re great, but together, you''re unstoppable. 
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(2732,1233,'EN','WWE SmackDown! vs. RAW 2009','');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(2733,1233,'FR','WWE Smackdown vs Raw 2009','WWE SmackDown vs. Raw 2009 ne faillit pas à la règle de la franchise qui est de proposer aux joueurs l''ultime simulation des matchs de catch de la WWE. WWE SmackDown vs. Raw 2009 pour Wii reprend tous les éléments qui ont fait le succès de la série et y ajoute son lot de nouveautés en développant considérablement les options de type de match, permettant ainsi aux joueurs de bénéficier pleinement de l''expérience de jeu intuitive, si caractéristique à la console de salon de Nintendo.
