INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(2948,1333,'EN','Wii Sports','Bundled with Wii, Wii Sports introduces a whole new way to play your game. This is what video games should be: fun for everyone. Wii Sports offers five distinct sports experiences, each using the Wii Remote controller to provide a natural, intuitive and realistic feel. To play a Wii Sports game, all you need to do is pick up a controller and get ready for the pitch, serve or that right hook. If you''ve played any of these sports before, you''re ready for fun!
