INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(3099,1405,'FR','Tony Hawk''s Downhill Jam','A vos skates pour goûter aux sensations extrêmes de la glisse dans Tony Hawk''s Downhill Jam. Entrez dans une compétition à haut risque et à très grande vitesse en dévalant les monts les plus abruptes du monde : du Machu Picchu et son terrain rocailleux aux rues goudronnées de San Francisco, entre autres sites uniques comme Hong Kong, Edimbourg et Rio de Janeiro.
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(3100,1405,'DE','Tony Hawk''s Downhill Jam','Schnapp dir dein Board und wage dich in die Welt der Extremsportarten in Tony Hawk’s Downhill Jam. In diesem halsbrecherischen Abfahrtswettbewerb rast du die steilsten Berge der Welt herunter – vom felsigen Terrain des Machu Picchu bis zu den Straßen von San Francisco. Zahlreiche andere Kulissen erwarten dich, darunter Hongkong, Edinburgh und Rio de Janeiro. 
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(3101,1406,'EN','Wacky World Of Sports','An outrageous sports game, Wacky World of Sports brings some of the world''s most obscure sports to the videogame world for the first time. The game takes players on a trip around the world to take part in some of the lesser known sports of countries like Italy, the Netherlands and Australia. The ten sports featured in the game all start easy enough but the more advanced a player becomes the more extreme the sports become! Tuna Tossing has been a popular sport down under for a number of years, but just how far can a tuna be thrown in the comfort of the living room? Drag out an old armchair to take part in Furniture Racing, but make sure Grandma is not still sitting in it because those chairs are fast! And if that''s still not bizarre enough, how about ironing a shirt while sky diving in the Extreme Ironing event?!');
