INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(3175,1439,'EN','Zack & Wiki: Quest For Barbaros'' Treasure','Puzzle solving has never been so fun! 
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(3176,1439,'FR','Zack & Wiki: Le Trésor de Barbaros','Entrez dans un monde d''énigmes et de pirates dans l''aventure de Zack & Wiki: le Trésor de Barbaros. Conçue par Capcom en exclusivité pour Wii, cette aventure "point-and-click" jonchée d''énigmes à résoudre mettra votre matière grise à contribution lorsque vous guiderez Zack et son acolyte Wiki le singe à travers des niveaux époustouflants pour retrouver un trésor perdu.
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(3177,1439,'DE','Zack & Wiki: Der Schatz von Barbaros','Begib dich bei dem Abenteuerspiel Zack & Wiki: Barbaros Schatz für die Wii in eine Welt der Puzzles und der Seeräuber. Im Hause Capcom ausschließlich für die Wii konzipiert, wirst du dir bei diesem Abenteuer, das wie ein Puzzle aufgebaut ist, bei dem man zielen und klicken muss, den Kopf zerbrechen, während du den angehenden Piraten Zack und seinen Kumpel Wiki, den Affen, auf der Suche nach unermesslichen Reichtümern durch Levels geleitest, die wahrlich ein Blickfang sind.
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(3178,1439,'ES','Zack y Wiki: En busca del Tesoro de Barbaros','El joven pirata Zack y su mascota Wiki, protagonizan esta aventura que les llevará a buscar un formidable tesoro oculto en una misteriosa isla. Montones de minijuegos y geniales puzles y un gran uso de las posibilidades del wiimote, destacan en este juego desarrollado por Capcom en exclusiva para Wii.
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(3179,1439,'IT','Zack & Wiki: Il Tesoro del Pirata Barbaros','');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(3180,1440,'EN','Winter Sports 2: The Next Challenge ','Winter Sports 2: The Next Challenge is an arcade oriented 3D simulation of only the most popular winter sports. The player is placed at the center of high level sporting events broadcast live around the world. The excitement of this major international competition is portrayed authentically with commentators, TV cameras and immersive environments. 
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(3181,1441,'EN','Winter Sports 2 The Next Challenge','');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(3182,1441,'FR','Winter Sports 2009: The Next Challenge','Winter Sports 2009 nous plonge dans la poudreuse grâce à ses 18 disciplines réparties dans 10 sports différents. Du snowboard, du ski, de la luge, du patinage, du curling, du saut, vous devriez normalement frissonner de plaisir si vous aimez le genre pendant que votre Wii, elle, vous réchauffera.');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(3183,1441,'IT','Winter Sports 2009: The Next Challenge','Grazie a Winter Sports 2009 potrai cimentarti negli sport invernali anche dal caldo confortevole del salotto di casa.
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(3184,1442,'EN','Summer Athletics: The Ultimate Challenge','Summer Athletics offers multiplayer fun for the entire family and brings the action and excitement of the most popular summer sporting disciplines right into your living room! The charming 3D comic style, varying levels of difficulty and intuitive controls will make Summer Athletics great fun for beginners and experts alike. Customize your character and develop your career as a professional athlete in career mode or challenge your friends in head-to-head competition.');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(3185,1443,'EN','Night at the Museum: Battle of the Smithsonian The Video Game','Get ready for a story so epic it could only unfold in the corridors of the world’s largest museum – the Smithsonian Institution. Museum guard-turned entrepreneur Larry Daley discovers that his favorite exhibits, and some of his best friends, from New York’s Natural History Museum are being shipped off to the archives at the Smithsonian. Larry gets a distress call from the miniature cowboy, Jedediah, reporting that Egyptian ruler Kahmunrah and a trio of heinous henchmen – namely Ivan the Terrible, Napoleon and Al Capone – are plotting to take over the museum, then the world. Speeding to the nation’s capitol, Larry is clearly in over his head. But with some impressive new pals, including the irrepressible Amelia Earhart, along with familiar friends Teddy Roosevelt and Octavius, Larry will stop at nothing to restore the Smithsonian before dawn.');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(3186,1444,'EN','Night at the Museum: Battle of the Smithsonian The Video Game','Get ready for a story so epic it could only unfold in the corridors of the world’s largest museum – the Smithsonian Institution. Museum guard-turned entrepreneur Larry Daley discovers that his favorite exhibits, and some of his best friends, from New York’s Natural History Museum are being shipped off to the archives at the Smithsonian. Larry gets a distress call from the miniature cowboy, Jedediah, reporting that Egyptian ruler Kahmunrah and a trio of heinous henchmen – namely Ivan the Terrible, Napoleon and Al Capone – are plotting to take over the museum, then the world. Speeding to the nation’s capitol, Larry is clearly in over his head. But with some impressive new pals, including the irrepressible Amelia Earhart, along with familiar friends Teddy Roosevelt and Octavius, Larry will stop at nothing to restore the Smithsonian before dawn.');
