INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(3427,1556,'EN','Pinball Hall of Fame: The Williams Collection','Back in the day, pinball was the game. Wannabe pinball wizards pumped in quarter after quarter and the best players became superstars in the arcade. Now you can relive those glory days with Pinball Hall of Fame - The Williams Collection.With true-to-life recreations of the hottest games from the 80''s, you can go full tilt ahead with the legends - including Pinbot, Firepower, and one of the all-time greats: Black Knight. And with the authentic game play, stunning visuals, and thrilling sound effects, you''ll swear you''ve been transported back to the arcade. ');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(3428,1557,'EN','Pinball: Hall Of Fame','Back in the day, pinball was the game. Wannabe pinball wizards pumped in quarter after quarter and the best players became superstars in the arcade. Now you can relive those glory days with Pinball Hall of Fame - The Williams Collection.With true-to-life recreations of the hottest games from the 80''s, you can go full tilt ahead with the legends - including Pinbot, Firepower, and one of the all-time greats: Black Knight. And with the authentic game play, stunning visuals, and thrilling sound effects, you''ll swear you''ve been transported back to the arcade.');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(3429,1558,'EN','Wild Earth: African Safari','Explore the wild and capture its natural beauty on film in Wild Earth: African Safari, a unique simulation for the Wii based on the PC game from Super X Studios. Take award-winning pictures of exotic animals in their natural habitats without disturbing them. From running with herds of zebra to following hunting lions and scavenging vultures, Wild Earth: African Safari lets you risk it all to capture and create magazine-quality pictorials! ');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(3430,1559,'EN','Wild Earth: African Safari','Explore the wild and capture its natural beauty on film in Wild Earth: African Safari, a unique simulation for the Wii based on the PC game from Super X Studios. Take award-winning pictures of exotic animals in their natural habitats without disturbing them. From running with herds of zebra to following hunting lions and scavenging vultures, Wild Earth: African Safari lets you risk it all to capture and create magazine-quality pictorials!');
