INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(3649,1663,'EN','Boom Blox Bash Party','Get ready for even more blox-busting action with BOOM BLOX Bash Party for Wii, the sequel to the critically-acclaimed BOOM BLOX game for Wii. Developed by EA in collaboration with director and producer Steven Spielberg, BOOM BLOX Bash Party takes destruction to new heights, providing the ultimate social gaming experience! BOOM BLOX Bash Party will get your party started with new Versus, Co-Op and Team Play challenges - twice as many multiplayer challenges as the original BOOM BLOX.
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(3650,1663,'ES','Boom Blox Bash Party','Mejorar la misma fórmula añadiendo novedades es una estrategia que no suele fallar. Al menos no debería si se cuida, como ha hecho Electronic Arts, todos y cada uno de los componentes que rodean el desarrollo de Boom Blox Bash Party, la continuación de aquel adictivo puzle eminemente pensado para el disfrute multijugador. Una física mejorada, más de 400 niveles para aburrir, nuevas animaciones y la misma premisa; hacer que los jugadores pasen un buen rato destruyendo bloques.');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(3651,1664,'EN','Boom Blox: Bash Party ','Get ready for even more blox-busting action with BOOM BLOX Bash Party for Wii, the sequel to the critically-acclaimed BOOM BLOX game for Wii. Developed by EA in collaboration with director and producer Steven Spielberg, BOOM BLOX Bash Party takes destruction to new heights, providing the ultimate social gaming experience! BOOM BLOX Bash Party will get your party started with new Versus, Co-Op and Team Play challenges - twice as many multiplayer challenges as the original BOOM BLOX.
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(3652,1664,'FR','Boom Blox: Smash Party','BOOM BLOX Smash Party sur Wii est un jeu de casse-boîtes virtuel imaginé par Steven Spielberg. Les joueurs doivent dégommer des blocs à l''aide de toutes sortes de projectiles pour accumuler des points et gagner des médailles. Il existe plus de 400 niveaux solos ou multijoueurs et il est possible de créer ses propres tableaux originaux dans un éditeur.');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(3653,1664,'DE','Boom Blox: Smash Party ','Von den Tiefen des Meeres bis in die unendlichen Weiten des Weltraums - in BOOM BLOX Smash Party kann man in mehr als 400 komplett neuen Leveln aufregende neue Themenwelten mit einzigartiger Physik und beeindruckender Grafik entdecken. Das Chaos lebt, während Puzzles unter Wasser oder in der Schwerelosigkeit gelöst und Explosionen ausgelöst werden. 
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(3654,1664,'ES','Boom Blox: Smash Party','Diversión garantizada para todas las edades.
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(3655,1664,'IT','Boom Blox: Smash Party','');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(3656,1664,'PT','Boom Blox: Smash Party','Prepara-te para mais acção Blox com Boom Blox™ Bash Party para a Wii™, a sequela do aclamado jogo Boom Blox™. Desenvolvido pela EA com a colaboração do director e produtor Steven Spielberg, Boom Blox™ Bash Party coloca a destruição em oito novos níveis, oferecendo a última geração experiência de jogos sociais! Boom Blox™ Bash Party oferece também novos modos multijogador, como os novos desafios Versus, Co-Op e Team Play, o dobro de desafios multijogador que o jogo original. Das profundezas do oceano até aos confins do espaço Boom Blox™ Bash Party apresenta mais de 400 novos níveis! Explora os novos temas com uma fantástica física e dramáticos visuais. Cria o caos, observa puzzles e explosões enquanto nadas debaixo de água ou flutoando em gravidade zero! Boom Blox™ Bash Party oferece também novas ferramentas e personagens. Experimenta o explosivo e destruitivo Vírus Blox ou o dançarino Conveyor Blox. Experimenta os novos desenhos como o Cylinders e Wedges ou usa as novas ferramentas Cannon e Slingshot para criar e lançar um blox! Agarra num dos personagens e coloca-o a voar! E a diversão continua online! Com novas capacidades, o jogo permite-te fazer o download de novos níveis apenas premindo um botão. A ligação é simples entre a tua Wii e a internet para escolher, jogar e classificar um dos novos níveis da EA e dos membros da comunidade Boom Blox™ Bash Party. Cria os teus próprios níveis utilizando a ferramenta Create, a mesma que a equipa de Boom Blox™ usou para criar o jogo! ');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(3657,1665,'EN','Pet Pals: Animal Doctor','You are the animal doctor at a busy veterinarian clinic and will need nurse all the animals back to health! The unique Wii Remote simulates real veterinary tools as you use them to treat 30 different cases, ranging from minor cases like sunburn, lacerations and infections to more serious problems like diabetes, tumors and snakebites. ');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(3658,1666,'EN','Pet Pals: Animal Doctor','Pet Pals: Animal Doctor is now available for the Wii!For the first time, players of all ages can bring the operating table right into their living room and enjoy a one of a kind gamin experience. The unique Wii controller simulates real veterinary tools as you use them to treat 30 different cases, ranging from minor cases like sunburn to more serious problems like tumors. Step in and have fun healing your favorite pets!
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(3659,1666,'DE','Pet Pals: Tierdoktor','Tierdoktor für die Nintendo Wii versetzt den Spieler in die Rolle eines Veterinärmediziners. Spieler aller Altersgruppen können mit Freude verschiedenste Tiere gesund zu pflegen. Die Beschwerden der kleinen, aber manchmal auch großen Racker reicht von Sonnenbrand und Infektionen bis hin zu schwerwiegenden Tumoren oder Schlangenbissen. Die Wii-Remote bietet hierfür einen leichten Einstieg.
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(3660,1667,'EN','Rygar: The Battle of Argus','Grab your “Diskarmor” and swing into action on the Wii as the legendary warrior, Rygar! Immerse yourself in Greco-Roman mythology as you journey through the sundered Island of Argus. Intuitive use of the Wii Remote allows you to deftly and effectively control the use of the powerful Diskarmor to destroy enemies and maneuver on, around, over, and under obstacles to save Princess Harmonia! 
