INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(3735,1707,'EN','The Legend of Zelda : Twilight Princess','When an evil darkness enshrouds the land of Hyrule, a young farm boy named Link must awaken the hero – and the animal – within. When Link travels to the Twilight Realm, he transforms into a wolf and must scour the land with the help of a mysterious girl named Midna. Besides his trusty sword and shield, Link will use his bow and arrows by aiming with the Wii Remote controller, fight while on horseback and use a wealth of other items, both new and old. ');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(3736,1707,'KO','젤다의 전설- 황혼의 공주','사악한 어둠이 하이룰의 영토를 휘감을때, 링크라는 이름의 젊은 소년이 자신속에 있는 영웅, 그리고 야수를 각성시켜야 한다. 링크가 여명의 땅을 여행할 때는, 늑대로 변신하여 미드나라는 신비한 소녀의 도움으로 영토를 지켜내야 한다. 믿음직한 칼과 방패와 함께 위 리모콘으로 조준하는 활과 화살로 말을 타고 싸우고 일부는 기존과 같으나 일부는 새로운 아이템을 사용하기도 한다.');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(3737,1708,'EN','The Legend of Zelda: Twilight Princess','When an evil darkness enshrouds the land of Hyrule, a young farm boy named Link must awaken the hero – and the animal – within. When Link travels to the Twilight Realm, he transforms into a wolf and must scour the land with the help of a mysterious girl named Midna. Besides his trusty sword and shield, Link will use his bow and arrows by aiming with the Wii Remote controller, fight while on horseback and use a wealth of other items, both new and old.');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(3738,1708,'FR','The Legend of Zelda: Twilight Princess','Lorsqu''un mal terrible se répand sur les terres d''Hyrule, c''est un jeune fermier prénommé Link qui doit réveiller le héros, et l''animal, qui sommeillent en lui.
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(3739,1708,'DE','The Legend of Zelda: Twilight Princess','"Als das Böse seine dunklen Schatten weit über die Grenzen von Hyrule ins friedliche Nachbarland verbreitet, erwacht ein junger Hirtenjunge - namens Link - zum Helden. Die letzten Fäden der Hoffnung liegen in Links Händen, das Böse - von seinem geliebten Ross aus - zu besiegen und seine Heimat zu verteidigen. Ein episches Abenteurer, das den Helden in unglaublicher Weise zu verwandeln vermag..."
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(3740,1708,'ES','The Legend of Zelda: Twilight Princess','El caos y la destrucción amenazan la paz de Hyrule y Link viaja a un nuevo mundo en el que puede adoptar la forma de lobo. Este es parte del argumento de esta nueva entrega de la famosa saga de Nintendo, que aunque originalmente fue creada para Gamecube, y que también llega a Wii aprovechando las novedosas opciones de control de esta consola.
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(3741,1709,'EN','Science Papa','Science Papa is the world''s most renowned scientist. You''ve just joined his elite team, and it''s time for you to prove your worth! Explore chemistry, physics, paleontology, and biology in over 30 different experiments. You''ll be competing against rival scientists who are out to steal prizes from under your nose. There are records to beat, lab equipment to unlock, and people to impress!  Mix chemicals, heat solutions, unearth dinosaur bones, and rewire electronic gadgets, all using the innovative control scheme. Take on the challenge of the Solo Mode, or attempt to sabotage your friends and family as you race to successfully complete different experiments!');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(3742,1710,'EN','Secret Files 2: Puritas Cordis','The world is on the brink of disaster. By the time Nina Kalenkow realizes that the recent catastrophes were caused not by nature, but by an unscrupulous secret society known as Puritas Cordis, it is almost too late. While her ex-boyfriend Max, a scientist, witnesses the brutal methods of Puritas Cordis at the excavation site of an ancient Indonesian temple complex, Nina joins forces with a priest in France to investigate the connection between the secret society''s sinister prophesies and the creepy leader of an ancient order. A dramatic race against time begins. Will the protagonists be able to avert the impending apocalypse?');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(3743,1710,'FR','Secret Files 2: Puritas Cordis','Secret Files 2: Puritas Cordis est la suite directe de l''aventure point''n click Secret Files: Tungunska sur Wii. Nous retrouvons l''héroïne Nina ainsi que Max qui enquêtent cette fois sur un prophète annonçant la fin des temps et sur des catastrophes naturelles survenant un peu partout dans le monde. Intrigues croisées, énigmes et réflexion sont au rendez-vous.');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(3744,1710,'DE','Geheimakte 2: Puritas Cordis','Der offizielle Nachfolger von Geheimakte Tunguska!
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(3745,1711,'EN','Zoo Hospital','You''ve graduated from Veterinary College not a moment too soon--your Aunt Lucy just called from the world famous Zoo Hospital she manages because she needs your help! A local property magnate, Gordon Grimm, is eying the zoo''s land as the potential site for a profitable mini-golf course. Under Aunt Lucy''s tutelage it''s now up to you to help restore the zoo to its former glory by treating its ailing inhabitants, improving its Zoo Rating and attracting new exotic animals that will in turn attract the crowds! ');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(3746,1712,'EN','Zoo Hospital','You''ve graduated from Veterinary College not a moment too soon--your Aunt Lucy just called from the world famous Zoo Hospital she manages because she needs your help! A local property magnate, Gordon Grimm, is eyeing the zoo''s land as the potential site for a profitable mini-golf course. Under Aunt Lucy''s tutelage it''s now up to you to help restore the zoo to its former glory by treating its ailing inhabitants, improving its Zoo Rating and attracting new exotic animals that will in turn attract the crowds! ');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(3747,1712,'FR','Zoo Hospital','Zoo Hospital sur Wii est une simulation dans laquelle votre but est de soigner tout un tas d''animaux. Au sein d''une équipe de vétérinaires, vous vous occupez à l''aide de votre Wiimote de près de 50 espèces d''animaux différents. Le jeu est l''occasion d''en apprendre plus sur les espèces en voie de disparition. Un mode deux joueurs en coopération vous permet de traiter les patients simultanément avec un ami.');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(3748,1713,'EN','Zoo Hospital','You''ve graduated from Veterinary College not a moment too soon--your Aunt Lucy just called from the world famous Zoo Hospital she manages because she needs your help! A local property magnate, Gordon Grimm, is eyeing the zoo''s land as the potential site for a profitable mini-golf course. Under Aunt Lucy''s tutelage it''s now up to you to help restore the zoo to its former glory by treating its ailing inhabitants, improving its Zoo Rating and attracting new exotic animals that will in turn attract the crowds! ');
