INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(3750,1713,'DE','Zoo Hospital','In Zoo Hospital wird die Wii-Fernbedienung zum medizinischen Instrument und der Bildschirm zum OP-Tisch.
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(3751,1714,'EN','Puzzle Kingdoms','From the acclaimed designer of Puzzle Quest, Steve Fawkner of Infinite Interactive, comes Puzzle Kingdoms. Deep, classic turn based empire gameplay tells an incredible story. Instead of auto-resolved conflict, a unique puzzle mechanic makes each battle unique and addictive.');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(3752,1715,'EN','Puzzle Kingdoms','Puzzle Kingdoms challenges players to plan out strategic attacks in order to defeat their opponents. Order troops across the map, conquering cities through innovative puzzle gameplay. Players build and manage armies led by heroic commanders to save the world of Etheria from the brink of destruction. By matching corresponding gems on the game board, players will both inflict damage on enemy forces while building mana that can be used to perform devastating attacks that will cripple their opponents.');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(3753,1715,'DE','Puzzle Kingdoms','Können Sie alle Geheimnisse des Königreichs aufklären? Puzzle Kingdoms garantiert Ihnen mit einem lebhaften Mix aus Fantasy, Strategie und Puzzlespielelementen ein einzigartiges und untersames Spielkonzept. Suchen Sie sich einen Helden, bauen Sie Ihre Armeen auf und erobern Sie neue Territorien um Zaubersprüche, Gegenstände und Einheiten freizuschalten. 
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(3754,1716,'EN','Link''s Crossbow Training','Anyone can pick up the Wii Zapper and become a master marksman in the quick-play shooting galleries of Link''s Crossbow Training. Dozens of fast-paced stages offer a wide variety of game play, from shooting stationary targets to defending a supply wagon from onrushing hordes of enemies. Multiplayer modes let players and their friends share a Wii Zapper to shoot for the high score.
