INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(3759,1718,'FR','Link''s Crossbow Training','Retournez à Hyrule pour vous entraîner à l''arbalète avec Link''s Crossbow Training sur Wii. Revisitez certains des lieux étonnants que vous aviez découverts dans The Legend of Zelda: Twilight Princess grâce à Link''s Crossbow Training, un jeu de tir plein d''action vendu exclusivement avec le Wii Zapper.
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(3760,1718,'DE','Link''s Crossbow Training','Kehren Sie nach Hyrule zurück und absolvieren Sie einmalige Zielübungen in Link’s Crossbow Training für die Wii. Dieses actionlastige Abenteuer findet an den Schauplätzen statt, die in The Legend of Zelda: Twilight Princess zum ersten Mal vorgestellt wurden. Die Spiele-Disc befindet sich exklusiv im Lieferumfang der Wii Zapper-Hardware.
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(3761,1719,'EN','The Destiny of Zorro','Players will make an incredible action-packed journey through the sun-scorched coast and desert landscape of early 1800’s Spanish California playing as the infamous Zorro – the swashbuckling defender of the oppressed whose secret identity is the fictional wealthy caballero Don Diego de la Vega.
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(3762,1720,'EN','The Destiny Of Zorro','Players will make an incredible action-packed journey through the sun-scorched coast and desert landscape of early 1800’s Spanish California playing as the infamous Zorro – the swashbuckling defender of the oppressed whose secret identity is the fictional wealthy caballero Don Diego de la Vega. 
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(3763,1720,'FR','La Destinée de Zorro','Endossez le costume du justicier renard dans le jeu d''action/aventure La Destinée de Zorro sur Wii. Découvrez petit à petit les origines du héros en remplissant des missions à l''aide de votre épée qui reproduit les mouvements de la Wiimote, y compris le fameux Z, signature mythique. Défendez les innocents, mettez votre lame au service de la veuve et l''orphelin, déjouez complots et rébellion dans la Californie des années 1800.');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(3764,1720,'DE','Das Schicksal des Zorro','Im Adventurespiel „Destiny of Zorro" machen Sie in der Rolle des Zorro eine unglaublich abenteuerliche Reise durch die sonnenversengte Küstenlandschaft des spanischen Kaliforniens. Als der legendäre Held kämpfen Sie für die Rechte der Armen und Unterdrückten und müssen so manchen bösartigen Widersacher mit allen Mitteln zur Strecke bringen. Diverse Spezialattacken sorgen in „Destiny of Zorro" für einen unvergleichlichen Spielspaß.');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(3765,1720,'ES','El Destino de El Zorro','¡El apasionante mundo del El Zorro en tu Wii!
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(3766,1720,'IT','Nel segno di Zorro','');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(3767,1720,'PT','Destiny Of Zorro','Em Destiny of Zorro, os fãs vão experimentar novas aventuras, ao mesmo tempo que revisitam as histórias e as personagens familiares do Zorro. O jogo decorre no início de 1800, na Califórnia Espanhola, no tempo do Zorro original, Don Diego de la Vega, com uma empolgante e nova estrutura, bem como personagens, que foram criadas especialmente para Destiny of Zorro. Utilizando as propriedades únicas do comando da Wii, os jogadores podem usar o chicote e claro, com um movimento, fazer a assinatura ‘Z’ do Zorro para fazer justiça. ');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(3768,1721,'EN','Speed Zone','A futuristic racing game for the Wii home video game system. Players can choose from three modes of play: Solo, Race, and Battle. In Race mode, players compete against seven computer-controlled AI cars, while Battle mode is an all-out, futuristic demolition derby, using spectacular weapon. In Solo mode, players try to ignite jet thrusters with boost pads to accelerate "into the zone," with phantom cars and racing lines to help set lap records.');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(3769,1722,'EN','Wii Sports Resort','Wii Sports Resort takes the inclusive, fun and intuitive controls of the original Wii Sports to the next level, introducing a whole new set of entertaining and physically immersive activities. With the deep control enhancements of Wii MotionPlus, veteran Wii users and newcomers alike can enjoy unprecedented gaming precision as they cruise on a water scooter, duel with swords, throw a Frisbee® and much more. This sequel to the popular Wii Sports makes use of the Wii MotionPlus accessory, which gives players the most responsive and realistic experience possible. The Wii MotionPlus accessory, which is included with Wii Sports Resort, plugs into the base of the Wii Remote™ controller and, combined with the accelerometer and sensor bar, provides an experience that gives players an even greater sense of immersion. Just as with Wii Sports, people will love competing against friends and family. As the competition heats up, Wii Sports Resort is as much fun to watch as it is to play. First-time players will find it easy to pick up a Wii Remote and jump into the action.');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(3770,1723,'EN','Wii Sports Resort','Wii Sports Resort takes the inclusive, fun and intuitive controls of the original Wii Sports to the next level, introducing a whole new set of entertaining and physically immersive activities. With the deep control enhancements of Wii MotionPlus, veteran Wii users and newcomers alike can enjoy unprecedented gaming precision as they cruise on a water scooter, duel with swords, throw a Frisbee® and much more. This sequel to the popular Wii Sports makes use of the Wii MotionPlus accessory, which gives players the most responsive and realistic experience possible. The Wii MotionPlus accessory, which is included with Wii Sports Resort, plugs into the base of the Wii Remote™ controller and, combined with the accelerometer and sensor bar, provides an experience that gives players an even greater sense of immersion. Just as with Wii Sports, people will love competing against friends and family. As the competition heats up, Wii Sports Resort is as much fun to watch as it is to play. First-time players will find it easy to pick up a Wii Remote and jump into the action.');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(3771,1723,'JA','Wiiスポーツ リゾート','Wiiの定番ソフトとして人気の高い「Wii Sports」に待望の続編が登場する。本作ではリゾートアイランド“ウーフーアイランド”を舞台にして、12のリゾート気分満点のスポーツを楽しむことができる。収録ゲームは“チャンバラ”“バスケットボール”“カヌー”“自転車”“マリンバイク”“ウェイクボード”“フリスビー”“アーチェリー”“ピンポン”“スカイレジャー”、そしてさらに「Wii Sports」で人気の高い“ゴルフ”“ボウリング”も本作でプレイ可能。もちろんWiiリモコンをそのスポーツに使う道具などに見立てての直感操作で楽しめる。最大4人同時プレイも楽しめるので、家族や友達を集めてワイワイと楽しもう。なお、本作は“Wiiモーションプラス”という周辺機器を使うことで、Wiiリモコンの動きを細やかに感知する。ソフトには“Wiiモーションプラス”が１つついており、同時プレイ時には参加人数分のWiiモーションプラス（別売）が必要となる。');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(3772,1723,'ZHTW','Wii運動 度假勝地','');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(3773,1724,'EN','Wii Sports Resort','Wii Sports Resort takes the inclusive, fun and intuitive controls of the original Wii Sports to the next level, introducing a whole new set of entertaining and physically immersive activities. With the deep control enhancements of Wii MotionPlus, veteran Wii users and newcomers alike can enjoy unprecedented gaming precision as they cruise on a water scooter, duel with swords, throw a Frisbee® and much more. This sequel to the popular Wii Sports makes use of the Wii MotionPlus accessory, which gives players the most responsive and realistic experience possible. The Wii MotionPlus accessory, which is included with Wii Sports Resort, plugs into the base of the Wii Remote™ controller and, combined with the accelerometer and sensor bar, provides an experience that gives players an even greater sense of immersion. Just as with Wii Sports, people will love competing against friends and family. As the competition heats up, Wii Sports Resort is as much fun to watch as it is to play. First-time players will find it easy to pick up a Wii Remote and jump into the action. ');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(3774,1724,'FR','Wii Sports Resort','Wii Sports Resort sur Wii est une nouvelle version du jeu vendu traditionnellement avec la console. Une série de nouveaux challenges vous attendent, utilisant pour certains le WiiMotion Plus, offrant plus de précision pour les mouvements de la manette. Le cadre est cette fois une île paradisiaque, sur laquelle vous allez pouvoir vous frotter au jet-ski, à de l''escrime ou encore à envoyer valser un freesbee pour que votre toutou virtuel le rattrape et vous le ramène.');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(3775,1724,'DE','Wii Sports Resort','Jetzt können Wii Spieler viele neue sportliche Aktivitäten auf einer tropischen Insel ausüben. Wie wäre es mit einer Runde Frisbee am Strand? Anschließend sorgt ein heißes Jet-Ski Rennen für die nötige Erfrischung. Wer es etwas beschaulicher mag, kann selbstverständlich auch ins Kanu steigen und sich paddelnd einen Weg durch das Wasser bahnen. Wii Sports Resort bietet abwechslungsreiche sommerliche Wettkämpfe, bei denen der Spaß immer im Mittelpunkt steht.
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(3776,1724,'ES','Wii Sports Resort','Titulo deportivo que sigue la linea de Wii Sports, incluyendo experiencias de juego como Sword Play, Power Cruising en una moto acuática y Disc Dog, entre otros. El juego se distribuye con el accesorio Wii MotionPlus y la Funda del mando de Wii sin coste adicional.
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(3777,1724,'IT','Wii Sports Resort','Benvenuti all''Arcipelago di Wuhu!
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(3778,1724,'PT','Wii Sports Resort','');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(3779,1725,'EN','Crayola Colorful Journey','From the creators of Crayola Treasure Adventures on DS and the most respected brand in households with kids, comes Crayola Colorful Journey Wii, the perfect game for all creative and adventurous boys and girls. Encouraging imagination and creativity, Crayola Colorful Journey Wii gives the player the ability to bring a virtual coloring book to life. Players will be transported into a world where they take on the role of either Fillup or Violet on a quest across Crayola Land. ');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(3780,1726,'EN','My Word Coach','Do you ever feel at "loss for words"? Would you like to express yourself more clearly and with confidence? Want to improve your vocabulary in a straightforward and entertaining way? In your daily life, knowing the right word can make all the difference! My Word Coach offers a fun and challenging way to improve verbal skills through a series of engaging activities and exercises. The game was inspired by ongoing vocabulary acquisition research by Thomas Cobb, University Professor in Applied Linguistics at the University of Quebec. Enjoyable activities include word recognition, spelling challenges, and vocabulary definition, including 16,800 words from the Cambridge Advanced Learner''s Dictionary.');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(3781,1727,'EN','My Word Coach: Develop your vocabulary','Do you ever feel at "loss for words"? Would you like to express yourself more clearly and with confidence? Want to improve your vocabulary in a straightforward and entertaining way? In your daily life, knowing the right word can make all the difference! My Word Coach offers a fun and challenging way to improve verbal skills through a series of engaging activities and exercises. The game was inspired by ongoing vocabulary acquisition research by Thomas Cobb, University Professor in Applied Linguistics at the University of Quebec. Enjoyable activities include word recognition, spelling challenges, and vocabulary definition, including 16,800 words from the Cambridge Advanced Learner''s Dictionary.');
INSERT INTO juego_descripcion VALUES(3782,1727,'FR','Mon coach personnel: j''enrichis mon vocabulaire','Mon Coach Personnel: J''enrichis mon Vocabulaire sur Wii vous permet de réduire vos fautes d''orthographe tout en vous amusant. La cartouche vous propose un programme d''entraînement personnalisé, adapté à votre niveau avec des exercices ludiques pour s''entraîner et s''amuser autour de plus de 16 500 mots accompagnés de leurs définitions. Un suivi de votre progression selon les objectifs que vous vous fixez est proposé de même qu''un mode multijoueur pour défier vos amis!');
